   <text:p text:style-name="P32">De-o sptmn ine-ntruna ploaia, <text:line-break/>i-mi pic-n pat, de sus, din bagdadie...<text:line-break/>O noapte nc de-ar mai fi s ie<text:line-break/>Nu m-a mira s-mi caz-n cap odaia!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Avea simptome vagi de nebunie<text:line-break/>Peninsula Balcanic... i d-aia,<text:line-break/>De cnd s-aprinse-n Orient vpaia,<text:line-break/>Pmntul face hidroterapie!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Sau poate c divinul Mizantrop<text:line-break/>A hotrt al doilea potop?...<text:line-break/>Oricum ar fi, eu nu m tem de moarte.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Dar cnd o-ncepe alt venicie,<text:line-break/>Fac cerere s m permute-n Marte,<text:line-break/>C-aici avem prea mult igrasie!</text:p>
