   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Sunt izolat ca Robinson Crusoe,<text:line-break/>Nu vine nime-n ua mea s bat,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i dac stau cu ua ncuiat<text:line-break/>E c nici eu de nime n-am nevoie.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Mai fericit ca legendarul Noe,<text:line-break/>Din toat omenirea inundat,<text:line-break/>n arca mea nu am dect o fat...<text:line-break/>Deasupra lumii noi plutim n voie...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Degeaba v-ndesai ca la poman,<text:line-break/>Reprezentani ai faunei terestre, <text:line-break/>Nu iau cu mine nici o lighioan!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Cci e destul o singur pereche:<text:line-break/>Un trubadur i-o fat fr zestre,<text:line-break/>Ca s refac toat lumea veche!</text:p>
