   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Din cpi sare pleav,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Sar gunoaie dintr-un snop.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Puca scoate fum pe eav</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i pornete ca un dop...</text:span></text:p>
