   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Trag cu ploaie n grmad,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Fr s intesc deloc...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cine s-atepta s-mi cad</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Patru iepuri dintr-un foc?...</text:span></text:p>
