   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Posomori, cu gheara lung,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu pliscuri negre de oel,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ne-am nfruptat ct s ne-ajung</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Din prnzul marelui Mcel.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu patrioii la parad,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Amestecai printre eroi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De-a valma coborm n strad, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar nu ne ducem la rzboi!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cnd geme-n vaier lung cmpia,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cnd stau ntori spre bolta crunt</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cei logodii cu venicia</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Sub ploaia rece i mrunt;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cnd moartea secer flmnd</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Fcnd mormane de eroi, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n dosul frontului, la pnd,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Noi nu ne ducem la rzboi!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Trziu, cu penele mnjite</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De snge negru  i stui,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n cuiburi calde i ferite</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ne-mperechem i scoatem pui</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ce s-or hrni ca i prinii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Din hoituri slabe de eroi, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cci, soli voioi ai suferinii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Noi nu ne ducem la rzboi!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Alte, zvonul crete iari,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Adun-i ceata de eroi...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu moartea suntem buni tovari,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar nu ne ducem la rzboi!</text:span></text:p>
