   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu cea din urm raz ce tremur-n amurg,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Se-ntunec palatul btrnului Habsburg.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">E noapte. Vntul toamnei aduce de departe</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Un freamt de suspine prin slile dearte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cci a pornit monarhul ncovoiat i chel</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Otiri din apte neamuri s moar pentru el!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Fclia lumineaz fantastice vitraiuri</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-n umbra colorat ca umbra din seraiuri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n linitea capelei pe-o treapt-ngenuncheat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu fruntea-n mini se roag btrnul mprat:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T14"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Stpne, codrii url i rurile gem,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Din fiece colib se-nal un blestem</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-n inima mea scurm prerile de ru!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Stpne, slobozete de-acum pe robul tu...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar vntul geme-n noapte:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">E prea trziu, btrne!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe arinile noastre de-a pururi va rmne</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Sinistr, ca o pnz de doliu, umbra ta.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">O, dac El te iart, noi nu te vom ierta!...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tresare mpratul. Micnd ncet din buze,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">ncearc s-i adune gndirile confuze...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar dou diamante strlucitoare curg</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">ncet-ncet pe nasul btrnului Habsburg,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-n linitea solemn, cum pic pe parchet,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Par dou lacrmi grele i mari  de spermanet.</text:span></text:p>
