   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Miu St. Popescu vrea s divoreze.<text:line-break/>Lung prilej de vorbe i de ipoteze!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Unii spun c Miu singur e de vin,<text:line-break/>C la ei n cas n-a fost zi senin.<text:line-break/>C nu poate nimeni s-i mai intre-n voie<text:line-break/>i-a avut norocul de-a gsit pe Zoe,<text:line-break/>Care-i rabd toate de cnd l-a luat.<text:line-break/>C desigur alta nu l-ar fi rbdat<text:line-break/>Nici mcar o lun, ns biata fat<text:line-break/>Este buntatea personificat!<text:line-break/>C-nainte Zoe pn nu-l luase<text:line-break/>A respins partide mult mai serioase:<text:line-break/>Jorj Athanasiu, cnd era flcu...<text:line-break/>Goldman de la Credit... Gu Popndu,<text:line-break/>Angrosist de vinuri,  o partid rar<text:line-break/>i cu care Miu nici nu se compar <text:line-break/>Toi cu situaii i destul de bine,<text:line-break/>Refuzai de dnsa, ca s ia... pe cine!<text:line-break/>C sraca Zoe cnd l-a cunoscut<text:line-break/>Era fr slujb i dator vndut.<text:line-break/>C de-atunci ncoace ea zadarnic sper,<text:line-break/>C el n-are-n cas nici o manier,<text:line-break/>Nu respect seara orele de mas,<text:line-break/>Rareori cu leafa nimerete-acas,<text:line-break/>Frecventeaz cele mai de jos localuri<text:line-break/>i se ine noaptea numai de scandaluri...<text:line-break/>Dar mai e un lucru mai fenomenal:<text:line-break/>Miu St. Popescu este imoral!<text:line-break/>Parc ea nu tie c, de-acum un an,<text:line-break/>Dumnealui se ine cu madam Vrlan?<text:line-break/>O caricatur... un chibrit... o aia<text:line-break/>Cu piciorul mare i c-un pr ct claia,<text:line-break/>O mahalagioaic... Afectat... rea, <text:line-break/>De se mir lumea: ce-a gsit la ea?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:soft-page-break/>Alii spun c totui nu-i de vin el,<text:line-break/>C din contra, Miu e un so model,<text:line-break/>ns ea, Popeasca, este o ingrat.<text:line-break/>C-ar fi stat i-acuma tot nemritat,<text:line-break/>Dac din pcate nu s-ar fi gsit<text:line-break/>Un neghiob ca Miu, un mbrobodit...<text:line-break/>C-a luat-o tocmai de pe la Vaslui<text:line-break/>Unde se dusese la un vr de-al lui<text:line-break/>Care-avea la dnii cas cu chirie.<text:line-break/>C vorbeau adesea la buctrie,<text:line-break/>Mai cu seam ziua cnd trecea la mas.<text:line-break/>C duduca Zoe scutura prin cas<text:line-break/>i  nu zice nimeni c era bigot <text:line-break/>ns franuzete nu tia o iot!<text:line-break/>C gsind odat nite cri franceze,<text:line-break/>A rugat pe Miu s-o iniieze...<text:line-break/>(Promitea fetia!) Tot aa mereu,<text:line-break/>Azi o srutare, mine... mai tiu eu?<text:line-break/>Ba cu franuzeasca, ba cu scuturatul,<text:line-break/>Pn cnd la urm a-ncurcat biatul!...<text:line-break/>Toate astea ns la un loc denot<text:line-break/>C-a luat-o goal, fr nici o dot.<text:line-break/>Trei perechi de case? tie Dumnezeu...<text:line-break/>Trei perechi de mofturi!  N-o spun numai eu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">ntrebai pe Lambru, pe madam Palade<text:line-break/>(O persoan-n vrst, foarte cumsecade)<text:line-break/>i pe toat lumea care-o cunotea,<text:line-break/>C-a luat-o numai cu ce-a fost pe ea...<text:line-break/>El putea desigur<text:span text:style-name="T1">altfel</text:span>s se-nsoare, <text:line-break/>Dar n loc s-i fie recunosctoare,<text:line-break/>S-l respecte-n cas i s-l menajeze,<text:line-break/>Dumneaei, din contra, ine s dicteze!<text:line-break/>Miu nu e liber nici mcar un pas,<text:line-break/>Toat lumea vede c l-a dus de nas.<text:line-break/>Dar n schimb, firete, ea, de la-nceput<text:line-break/>Fr nici o jen a fcut ce-a vrut.<text:line-break/>Seara, cnd o caui, pleac la cucoane,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Ziua se ocup numai cu romane,<text:line-break/>Iar buctreasa (c-au schimbat femeia)<text:line-break/>Are tot pe mn, pn cnd i cheia<text:line-break/>De la magazie i de la dulap, <text:line-break/>Care va s zic i-a fcut de cap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Alii spun c Zoe, la madam Lipan,<text:line-break/>A-ntlnit pe unu, Iorgu Damian, <text:line-break/>Flutur de saloane, mare pulama.<text:line-break/>C-ntre ei desigur exista ceva,<text:line-break/>Fi&apos;ndc ea-ntr-o clip de sinceritate<text:line-break/>A scpat o vorb la madam Stamate:<text:line-break/>Ah,<text:span text:style-name="T1">ma chre</text:span>, ce nobil i distins biet!...<text:line-break/>Iar madam Stamate n-a inut secret,<text:line-break/>i-i destul s afle cteva persoane...<text:line-break/>Tot atunci, se vede, una din cocoane<text:line-break/>I-a fcut pesemne lui o anonim<text:line-break/>Unde isclise doar att: Cu stim...<text:line-break/>i-i scria acolo  spun din auzite <text:line-break/>C madam Popescu prea se compromite...<text:line-break/>Dar el n-a citit-o, nefiind francat.<text:line-break/>i-a trecut i asta.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/><text:tab/><text:tab/></text:span>n sfrit, odat<text:line-break/>Trebuind s plece Miu la Vaslui<text:line-break/>Pentru nite case,  un amic de-al lui,<text:line-break/>Unul de la Banc, l-a pornit cu sila<text:line-break/>S ia trenul numai pn la Chitila<text:line-break/>i s stea acolo tocmai timpul strict,<text:line-break/>Ca s-i poat prinde n flagrant delict...<text:line-break/>C venind Popescu i vznd lumin,<text:line-break/>A intrat n curte tocmai prin grdin<text:line-break/>i btnd la ua care d-n salon,<text:line-break/>Cineva din cas i-a strigat: Pardon!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Zoe sta de vorb, nici nu s-atepta<text:line-break/>(C era devreme... zece i ceva)<text:line-break/>i creznd c-i ma sau vrun alt ecou,<text:line-break/>Cnd vzu c-i Miu, a rmas tablou,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>El pru deodat foarte ncntat.<text:line-break/> M iertai  le zise  c v-am deranjat!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Puse-apoi paltonul peste geamantan<text:line-break/>i venind cu-ncetul ctre Damian<text:line-break/>Care sta s plece, zise:  Bun seara.<text:line-break/>(Damian atuncea s-a fcut ca ceara.)<text:line-break/>Nu mai stai de vorb? Poate c i-e somn...<text:line-break/>Te grbeti prea tare, mult stimate domn!<text:line-break/>i zicnd acestea cu o voce calm,<text:line-break/>Vru s-l ia de guler i s-i dea o palm.<text:line-break/> Domnule Popescu... nene! stai un pic...<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pe parola noastr c n-a fost nimic!...</text:span><text:line-break/>Damian, sracul, nu tia ce zice, <text:line-break/>Dar gsind la urm un moment propice,<text:line-break/>Cnd vzu c treaba tot mai ru se-ncurc,<text:line-break/>A fugit...<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/><text:tab/></text:span>Iar soii se certar furc.<text:line-break/>Ea-l lua cu bine, nu-l scotea din drag,<text:line-break/>Socotind c astfel va putea s-o dreag,<text:line-break/>Dar la urma urmei, ca s-l deie gata,<text:line-break/>A-nceput s fac, ea, pe suprata.<text:line-break/>C odinioar l-a iubit un pic,<text:line-break/>Dar nu-l cunoscuse chiar aa mojic...<text:line-break/>i-ntorcnd o clip capul ndrt,<text:line-break/>I-a strigat din u:  Te-ai prostit di tt!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P28">*</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">Toate astea ns n-au nici un temei,<text:line-break/>C nu tie nimeni ce-a fost ntre ei.<text:line-break/>Vineri toat lumea a putut s-i vad<text:line-break/>Amndoi alturi, bra la bra, pe strad...<text:line-break/>Ei, i tii, asear, dup ce-a stat ploaia,<text:line-break/>Ce-a aflat Tnica de la Procopoaia<text:line-break/>Cnd s-a dus s-i cear un model de or?...<text:line-break/>C madam Popescu nu mai d divor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P64"><text:soft-page-break/>1911</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Dedicaie</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">1924</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Lira spnzurat-n cui</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cam de mult am prsit-o,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De urtul tu, iubito,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i de dragul nimnui.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Degetele-mi amorite</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De-abia lunec pe strune.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Toate coardele sunt bune,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Doar a&apos; inimii-s plesnite.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pentru tine, adorato,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Vreau s-mi cnt de azi ncolo</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Bucuriile-n tremolo</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i tristeea-n pizzicato.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">i de s-o-ntmpla ca tonul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ori msura s nu-i plac,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Vom ntoarce patefonul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i vom pune alt plac.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Gelozie</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dac nu ne-am fi-ntlnit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">(Absolut din ntmplare),</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tu pe altul oarecare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tot aa l-ai fi iubit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dac nu-i ieeam n drum,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ai fi dat cu bucurie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Altuia strin, nu mie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Mngierile de-acum.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ai avea i vreun copil</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Care, poate (idiotul!),</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ar fi smnat n totul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu-acel tat imbecil.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar aa... ce lucru mare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">C-ntr-o zi ne-am ntlnit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i c-s foarte fericit, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Absolut din ntmplare!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Popular</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ah, rzboiul blestemat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cte vduve-a lsat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n durere  i ci prunci</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Au rmas orfani de-atunci!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar cnd stai s te gndeti,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Toate cele pmnteti</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Sunt ca umbra norilor,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ca mireasma florilor.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Nu-i mirare c, de-atunci,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Au crescut srmanii prunci</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i vd nc soarele</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Toate vduvioarele...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Doar pe morii din rzboi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Putrezii n vnt i-n ploi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">N-are cine-i ntreba</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dac-s fericii ori ba.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Toamna n parc </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cad grbite pe aleea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Parcului cu flori albastre</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Frunze moarte, vorba ceea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ca iluziile noastre.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Prin lumina estompat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De mtasa unui nor,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Vistoare trece-o fat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">C-un plutonier-major.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Rumen de timiditate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">El se uit-n jos posac.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ea strivete foi uscate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Sub pantofii mici de lac.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-ntr-o fin discordan</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu privelitea sonor,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Merg aa, cam la distan,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">El major i ea minor...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Balada unei stele mici </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">ii minte tu, iubita mea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">O noapte de argint n care</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Mi-ai artat pe cer o stea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Din Carul mare?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu faa-n sus, spre Dumnezeu</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Lsndu-i capul s se culce</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe braul meu</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Te legnam, povar dulce</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Deasupra noastr, un castan</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu frunze pudic rsfirate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pentru-a servi de paravan</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Iubirilor nevinovate</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tinznd o ramur-n zadar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ca s ne apere de stele</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Fusese martor ocular</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">La toate cele</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">i nu mi-ai spus atunci nimic</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar cnd mi-am coborat privirea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Un deget mic</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Mi-a artat Nemrginirea</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Un strop de-argint a lunecat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i, cu paloare-i sideral</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe cerul negru a-nsemnat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Un fir subire de beteal.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">ii minte ce fior strin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Trecu atunci, din constelaii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Prin bluza ta de </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T12">crpe-de-Chine</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu aplicaii?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ce veti din cerul deprtat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">A nins pe fruntea ta zenitul?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ce gnduri tainice-ai schimbat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T8">I</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">nfinitul?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Sclipind departe, prin frunzi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">O stea smerit i albastr</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Sta singuratic, piezi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Deasupra noastr</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T8"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">i ca un spin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu raza-i rece i subire</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Mi-a strecurat un gnd strin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n visul meu de fericire.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Zicea: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T8"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6"> Subt cerul vast i mut</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">V-a aruncat aceeai soart</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe-un strop de lut</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ce-n nvrtirea lui v poart.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Srman atom sentimental</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Nu tii tu oare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">C viaa voastr-i colosal</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">De trectoare?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Zicea:  M mir c te-ai gndit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">S-mi cni o od.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De cnd poeii s-au prostit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Amorul nu mai e la mod.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Oricum, voi suntei prea mruni</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">i eu prea mare </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">N-ar fi mai bine s renuni</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i s v ducei la culcare?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">C nu exist pe pmnt</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Mai venerabil manie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dect  sub stele jurmnt</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe venicie.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">i nu exist-n univers</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Mai mare crim</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dect  la coada unui vers</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">S pui o rim </text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>n Iai </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dou, post-meridiane...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Sun lung i monoton</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ornicul cu trei cadrane</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De la Sfntul Spiridon.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Toamna prin vzduh adie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ca un zbor de libelul.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n lumina strvezie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Merge-agale o patrul.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe trotuarul plin de soare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Salt-n mers grbit perechi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De studente zmbitoare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu frizete la urechi,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">i spre Universitate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Trec, ducnd pe serviete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Clariti ntunecate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i sclipiri de baionete.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Expunere de motive </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Epigraph">Pentru ce n-am concurat niciodat la premiile Academiei.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">nti, fiindc mi-a fost lene...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Al doilea, nu-s modernist</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Sentimental ca Demostene</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i nici ca Blaga  futurist...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Al treilea, mi-e imposibil:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Eu dezaprob i versul chiop</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i orice premiu divizibil...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Al patrulea  sunt mizantrop.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Al cincilea, din fudulie...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Al aselea, fiindc n-am</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">ncredere-n Academie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i nici la cine s-o reclam...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Al aptelea,  mi-a fost ruine...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Al optulea, n-aveam nici eu</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Prere bun despre mine...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Al noulea, mi vine greu</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">S m prezint cu opu-n mn</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe la ilutrii mei confrai</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Din Academia Romn,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S zic: E bun  mi-l premiai?...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Al zecelea, nu pot admite</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S fiu nvins la handicap </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i cnd m-ar scoate din srite</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Le-a da, pardon, cu opu-n cap!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Al unsprezecelea,  valuta</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Reduce-o parte din talent.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cnd mia face azi ct suta,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ori dai un spor echivalent,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ori tragi oblonul la fereastr...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-al doisprezecelea  nu pot,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Fiindc printre dumneavoastr</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">E unul crn i idiot</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6"><text:note text:id="ftn29" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>29</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
       <text:p text:style-name="P37">Aluzie la criticul smntorist Bogdan Duic, unul dintre membrii Academiei, care era mpotriva premierii lui Toprceanu.</text:p></text:note-body></text:note></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cocostrcul albastru </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Epigraph">Cu prilejul intrrii d<text:span text:style-name="T24">-</text:span>lui <text:line-break/>Mihail Sadoveanu la Academie</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Rsun cobza i vioara,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Fac gospodinele pomeni...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ce chef la noi n Viioara,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ce praznic mare-n Rdeni!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Chiar Hanul-Boului nvie!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Iar jos, la Crma lui mo Precu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">E-atta zvon i veselie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De parc azi se las secu!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">La vod-Toma vin rzeii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S afle astzi crezmnt.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">oimaru bea cu megieii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Izbind cciulile-n pmnt</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe cnd Duduia Margareta,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Rmas singur-n ietac</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S-i fac-n grab toaleta,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S-a-mpuns la deget cu un ac...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Vuiesc pe Bistria nahlapii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i cnt volbura la Toance.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Plutaii drzi, n sforul apei,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">nfig prjina, ca o lance.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Spre-o lume care-a fost odat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Duc vestea undele-n rspr...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">St Zna Lacului mirat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">C-un nufr galben prins n pr...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe grindul unui lac sihastru,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Din deprtri i din trecut</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Un mndru Cocostrc albastru</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Misterios a aprut...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">El vine cu micri atente,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">nainteaz fr glas,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Fcnd uoare complimente</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Din cap, la fiecare pas.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-n urm zice ctre Zn,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Oprindu-se ntr-un picior:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T14"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cnd falnic m-am lsat din zbor</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe Academia Romn,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Eram demult nemuritor...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">1921</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Poetul</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Frumos ca un erou de melodram,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">El se expune-n poze studiate:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Profil... </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T12">trois-quarts</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">... din fa... de la spate.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i tuturor surde ca o dam.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">tiu pn i varditii cum l cheam,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">A devenit o personalitate.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cotidiana lui celebritate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ca un balon se umfl din reclam.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">i scrie... scrie... i nimic nu terge,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Avnd mereu impresia c merge</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i c-ntr-o zi va cuceri Parnasul.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Zadarnic, totdeauna, la intrare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu politee i se taie nasul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">C-i crete iar, din ce n ce mai mare!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Scrisoare</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:line-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Epigraph">Rspuns<text:span text:style-name="T24"> d-lui Al. O. Teodoreanu</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">...Ba mata eti tip ridicol!<text:line-break/>Eu n-am scris nici un articol<text:line-break/>ntru aprarea Muzii,<text:line-break/>Despre cel care<text:line-break/>Pare<text:line-break/>C-mi faci treizeci de aluzii...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Criticul pe care-aici<text:line-break/>l ataci n versuri mici<text:line-break/>Nu-i, desigur, mscrici,<text:line-break/>Colibri sau licurici...<text:line-break/>ns nici<text:line-break/>Bou sau vac, precum zici.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P63">E profesor (onorabil),<text:line-break/>Autor (interminabil),<text:line-break/>Om politic (execrabil),<text:line-break/>Critic (foarte vulnerabil,<text:line-break/>Dar pasabil),<text:line-break/>Preedinte (incurabil)<text:note text:id="ftn30" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>30</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
      <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:s/><text:span text:style-name="T25">Aluziile lui Toprceanu vizeaz pe criticii M. Dragomirescu i Eugen Lovinescu</text:span></text:p></text:note-body></text:note>.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Cnd i laud ciracii,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i compar cu toi dracii.<text:line-break/>Fr spirit diplomatic,<text:line-break/>Cu-ale lui precepte<text:line-break/>Drepte,<text:line-break/>Are cioc, dar e simpatic.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P25">*</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Cel pe care-n adevr<text:line-break/>L-am luat cndva-n rspr<text:line-break/>E un tip mai fistichiu.<text:line-break/>Cnd l iei n prip,<text:line-break/>ip...<text:line-break/>Las-m s i-l descriu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Are-o mutr anodin<text:line-break/>De frizer cu mandolin,<text:line-break/>O privire clandestin,<text:line-break/>Nas de parafin<text:line-break/>Fin,<text:line-break/>i la gur vaselin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Bra rotund i crup plin,<text:line-break/>Organism de gelatin,<text:line-break/>Cu structur androgin, <text:line-break/>Iar la-nfiare<text:line-break/>Pare<text:line-break/>O statuie de slnin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">i mai are... Ce mai are?<text:line-break/>Cnd se duce la culcare<text:line-break/>E de genul feminin,<text:line-break/>Dar cnd scrie proz<text:line-break/>Roz,<text:line-break/>Isclete masculin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">n al Criticii domeniu<text:line-break/>Orice Eu se crede geniu,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Dac-i secondat de proti...<text:line-break/>Alte semnalmente?<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Niente!</text:span><text:line-break/>Trebuie s-l recunoti.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P25">*</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Deci scriind el prin reviste<text:line-break/>Cronici impresioniste<text:line-break/>Cu dantele mprejur,<text:line-break/>ntr-o zi i-a zis c<text:line-break/>Risc<text:line-break/>S rmie prea obscur.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Cum avuse ara pace,<text:line-break/>El iei din carapace,<text:line-break/>i cu pagini din rzboi,<text:line-break/>Dup-acel masacru<text:line-break/>Sacru,<text:line-break/>S-a vrt printre eroi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">tiu, pe astfel de specimeni<text:line-break/>Astzi nu-i condamn nimeni,<text:line-break/>Au ajuns la apogeu.<text:line-break/>Ei, dar sta s m-nfrunte?...<text:line-break/>Pun&apos;te<text:line-break/>Un moment n locul meu!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">C m tie fiecare,<text:line-break/>Sunt sfios ca fata mare<text:line-break/>i blajin de obicei, <text:line-break/>ns cnd m apr<text:line-break/>Scapr<text:line-break/>Ca din cremene scntei!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">n cuptor mi vr colacii<text:line-break/>Cnd s-arat vrcolacii.<text:line-break/>Spada-mi gata de atac,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Luminoas ca o dr,<text:line-break/>Vr<text:line-break/>Spaima-n orice vrcolac!</text:p>
   <text:list xml:id="list2128938225" text:style-name="L23">
    <text:list-header>
     <text:p text:style-name="P86">*</text:p>
    </text:list-header>
   </text:list>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Ce folos avui de-acolo?...<text:line-break/>Cu sgeata lui Apollo<text:line-break/>n zadar l-am sgetat,<text:line-break/>Cci o epiderm<text:line-break/>Ferm<text:line-break/>Este greu de perforat...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Nimeni pace nu-i d dac<text:line-break/>Ai nevoie de ddac.<text:line-break/>Dragul meu, de-aceea zic<text:line-break/>C scriind sudalme<text:line-break/>Calme<text:line-break/>Nu poi ctiga nimic.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Ci, mai bine,  Muzei cale<text:line-break/>S-i deschizi cu muzicale<text:line-break/>Rime, ca de obicei, <text:line-break/>Iar pe pr s-i scuturi<text:line-break/>Fluturi<text:line-break/>De imagini i idei.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">1922 </text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Ripost</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="Epigraph">Unui gazetar<text:note text:id="ftn31" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>31</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
      <text:p text:style-name="P22">Se refer la Octavian Tsloanu, aflat n polemic, pe atunci, cu Toprceanu. n 1919 conducea revista <text:span text:style-name="T2">Luceafrul</text:span>.</text:p></text:note-body></text:note> care cerea s fie spnzurat</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:soft-page-break/>Vrei s m spnzuri, vaszic?...<text:line-break/>Cnd te-am citit, n adevr,<text:line-break/>i dau cuvntul c de fric<text:line-break/>Mi s-a zbrlit un fir de pr!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Cum? i-a venit aa, deodat,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/><text:tab/></text:span>Netam-nesam?<text:line-break/>Preai un om cu judecat <text:line-break/>La asta nu m ateptam.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Te-ai suprat i-i pare ru<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/><text:tab/></text:span>C-s nc viu?<text:line-break/>Pcat c eti de la Tazlu,<text:line-break/>Pcat c trebuie s-i scriu!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Dar asta-i datoria mea:<text:line-break/>S dau cu zacherlin-n proti.<text:line-break/>Talent avem  o recunoti.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/><text:tab/></text:span>Atunci, pzea!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Pzea, s nu dai de ruine,<text:line-break/>S nu te strng ntr-un sonet.<text:line-break/>S nu te spnzur eu pe tine<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/><text:tab/></text:span>De-un epitet!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Pzea, c muza mi-i fecund<text:line-break/>i cnd te-oi prinde nu te scap:<text:line-break/>Cu apte rime pe secund<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/><text:tab/></text:span>i dau la cap!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Pzea, s nu te-atern pe-o fil<text:line-break/>i-n roca unui vers masiv<text:line-break/>S te-ncrustez definitiv<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/><text:tab/></text:span>Ca pe-o fosil!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Pzea, s nu-i nfig n coast<text:line-break/>O epigram ca un cui.<text:line-break/>S-i sparg n cap o od proast,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/><text:tab/></text:span>S faci cucui!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">S nu-i arunc n ochi o stan<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/><text:tab/></text:span>Cu versuri mici,<text:line-break/>S nu te ard de la distan<text:line-break/>C-un hexametru ca un bici!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">i-apoi, n hazul galeriei,<text:line-break/>C-un vers subire ca un ac,<text:line-break/>Pe frontispiciul Veniciei<text:line-break/>S te fixez ca pe-un gndac!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">1919</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Bene merenti </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Epigraph">Cu prilejul decorrii dlui Ibrileanu</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Credeam c-i numai o poveste.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cnd colo este</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Adevrat!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Aflai asear trista veste...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Eu am pe cap proiecte grele</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu care lupt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar vestea asta m-a-ntrerupt</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Din ocupaiile mele.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T8"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">i la moment</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Mi-am zis: S-i fac vreo dou stane,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S-i telegrafiez urgent</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Condoleane...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Citesc i recitesc misiva,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Nedumerit m uit la plic</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">i nu-mi explic:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ai publicat ceva-n Arhiva? ...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Te-i fi aflat cndva-n eclips</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-ai scris un studiu analitic?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Sau poate Spiritului critic</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">I-or fi gsit vreo lips?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cum a putea descoperi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Mainria?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S tii c N. N. Zaharia</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">A isclit ceva: G. I.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Sau alt pan anonim</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Te-a ludat cumva la Motru?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pcat c n-am aici o rim</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">n </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T12">otru</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">(Vezi, eu... cu toate c n-am dat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Lucrri mai vaste,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Am scris destule versuri proaste</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i totui nu m-au decorat.)</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar trebuie s lmurim</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Acest mister...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Nu ai cumva vrun omonim,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Funcionar la minister?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">S tii c-aici e-ncurctura!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Eu i spuneam</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">C toi acetia se cam</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ocup cu literatura...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ai vreo protecie de fust?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">O, a putea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S-i fac aluzie... dar nu st</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">n firea mea.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">...Degeaba caut nainte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">C nicidecum</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Nu-mi vine-n minte...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">M-am ntrebat i azi pe drum,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">M-ntreb i-acum, cnd stau alene</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu braele sub cpti:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De ce te-au decorat cu Bene</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Merenti clasa I?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Da, tiu c te-a-njurat la </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T12">Noua</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2"><text:line-break/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T12">Revist</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6"> tipul clandestin...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar cel puin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S i-o fi dat de clasa a II-a!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ce? Ai ucis pe cineva?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">O, dimpotriv,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Nu ai alur ofensiv...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ce-or fi avut cu dumneata?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">C ziua-i obloneti odaia,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Nici nu te-auzi, nici nu te vezi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-n toate nopile veghezi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ca cucuvaia.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">nct ne speriem acum</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cnd i zrim pe strad mutra,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De parc ne-ntlnim n drum</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu Brahmaputra!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ci mulumete-te ncalte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">C-un singur hap.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cci omului i vin i alte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Nenorociri mai mari pe cap.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ce-ai zice dac, bunoar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T24"><text:tab/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">ntr-o privin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Te vor distinge-a doua oar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T12">Brbie i credin</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T13"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">?...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_1" text:outline-level="1">Din periodice</text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Furtuna</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P49"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Nimeni n-a rmas n strad.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Norii negri vin grmad.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Zboar frunzele uscate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n vzduh mprtiate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i salcmii stau s cad:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Bate vntul, bate...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">A ieit de la rscruce</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">O femeie care duce</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Un copil de mn... Sun</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pori izbite de furtun</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i femeia face cruce:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Fulger i tun.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar a norilor nfram</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Se sfie... Biata mam,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu puterile sczute,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Vrea copilul s-i ajute</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i cu glas pierdut l cheam:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T14"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Hai cu mama, iute!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">L-a luat acum n brae.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ploaia o izbete-n fa.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Bolta parc-i spart-n dou...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu mnuele-amndou</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">El de gtul ei s-aga:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T14"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Plou, mam, plou!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Lacul</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">n grmezi greoaie, norii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dintr-o parte strbtur</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i de chipul lor ptruns,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Faa lacului e sur.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Lng ap, singuratic,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Plopul trist, fr vemnt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Jeluindu-i frunza moart</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Se ndoaie dup vnt.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pleac unde dup unde</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i micarea lor domoal</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Colo-n trestie ptrunde,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Legnnd o luntre goal...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Mult a vrea n feeria</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Unei nopi de mai, senine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S plutesc pe apa-i clar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu iubita lng mine,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">i a undelor poveste</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Nesfrit, s-o ascult...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar aa, cum eti acuma,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Lacule, mi placi mai mult!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Vin, iubito </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P49"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Prin dumbrav se strecoar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Vnt de var,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i cocorii, ir pribeag,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n adnc senin plutesc.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cnt cucu n huceag:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cucule, ci ani triesc?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">mbrcatu-s-au n floare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De ninsoare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pomii toi de prin livezi.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Rul lunec pe prund</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Aa limpede c-i vezi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pietricelele din fund.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Jos, n umbr de rchite,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tinuite</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Viorele s-au ivit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-n pr negru la femei</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ct de albi au nflorit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Parfumaii ghiocei!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Vin, iubito! O poveste</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Trist este</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Viaa noastr cnd s-a stins,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar e rai cnd o trim.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Vino! Domnul dinadins</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ne-a fcut s ne iubim:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">A pus vara n dumbrav</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-a zis: Na-v</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Crngul plin de cnttori,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i copacii nverzii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i poienile cu flori</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Vi le dau s v iubii!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Terine</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P49"><text:span text:style-name="T6">i acum in minte oaptele-i pierdute</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n vuietul slbatic de furtun:<text:line-break/></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">De ce nu eti cuminte? Du-te, du-te!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">E vnt, e noapte. Fulger i tun,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-o ploaie  acum a nceput s cad</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n picuri mari ct boaba de alun.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cuprinsu-i plin ca de sclipiri de spad,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Eu plec ncet, ca-n vis, i nu-mi dau seam.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Un glas... dar cine-ar fi putut s cread?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Prea c-n urm-mi rugtor m cheam.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">O noapte </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P49"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe cerul plin de stele nori negri se atern</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">ntunecnd deodat al nopii far etern.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">O umbr fioroas nvluie pmntul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-n pacea nopii negre, vuind s-aude vntul.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Mai fi-vor pentru mine vrodat nopi cu lun?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Furtun e afar i-n pieptul meu  furtun.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Sclipesc fulegere repezi pe ceru-ntunecat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cum gnduri repezi, noaptea, din suflet mi-o strbat.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i tunetul s-aude gemnd n deprtare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cum geme-ntr-al meu suflet eterna desperare.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Btut de vnturi, codrul pustiu i jalnic sun.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Furtun e afar i-n pieptul meu  furtun.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Pcatul</text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="P55" text:outline-level="4">I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Trist vjie vntul i crengile-ndoaie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n negur cnt al codrilor glas</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i calul strbate, prin pnze de ploaie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Drum fr lumin i fr popas...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Un fulger deasupra tresare o clip,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Se vd nouri vinei pe cerul cernit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i pasrea nopii slbatic ip</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De spaim, cu glasul prelung, ascuit.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i iptul jalnic rsun departe,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ecou-l repet cu sute de guri. </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Adnc rspndete o spaim de moarte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Plutind peste-ntinderi de negre pduri...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Noaptea-i oarb, vntul bate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ploaia pic-n picuri reci,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Fulgerele deprtate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dau lumin pe poteci.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">La apus, din vreme-n vreme,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tunetul departe geme, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Du-te, du-te, nu te teme!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Noaptea-i neagr,  lass fie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">C-i arat drumul greu</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Doi ochi negri  i te-mbie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S te duci spre ei, mereu.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pentru ochii de crbune,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Iadu-n cale de s-ar pune,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Spaima lui nu te-o rpune.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i de ploaie nu te plnge,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Brae albe cnd te-or strnge,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Simi n vine foc, nu snge!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4">II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Vuind prelung se-ntinde a clopotelor jale</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n pacea nopii negre. La vechea mnstire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Chiliile  btrne zidiri medievale </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n sunetul de clopot tresar din amorire.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Din linitea chiliei, prin ferestruici boltite,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Strbate-n ntuneric o palid lumin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tiat-n dungi de groase zbrele ruginite,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i liliacul nopii, cu aripa lui fin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">O spintec n zborul cotit,  apoi dispare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">ipnd n ntuneric. Rsar de prin chilii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Clugrie  negre fantome solitare </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu haine lungi, cernite, purtnd n mini fclii.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Biserica nalt ncepe s rsune,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Curg note tnguioase n linitea adnc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i lin plutind n noapte cntri de rugciune</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Se-ntorc i se repet, lovite-n zid de stnc.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4">III</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">.......................</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T14"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Epifnio, cnd toaca te deteapt la utrenii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i cnd maicile vin toate s se roage la altar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pentru ce stai n iatacul ncrcat de mirodenii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Urmrind, prin ntuneric, voluptoasele vedenii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Care rnd pe rnd dispar?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n tcerea din odaie, ale gndurilor oapte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i rsun-ncet n suflet, ca un cntec adormit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Din trecutul tu crmpeie de icoane i de fapte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ca prin vis le desfoar a uitrii neagr noapte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Parc altul le-a trit...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">A ascuns n tine Domnul un tezaur de virtute,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar i-a dat ochi plini de visuri, negri, mari, cu gene lungi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-a sdit n snge smbur de dorini necunoscute,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">O, credina ta e mare, dar cu-attea nopi pierdute,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Maic, unde vrei s-ajungi?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Trupul tu plin de via n-a tiut ce e iubirea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Gura ta nesrutat numai sfini a srutat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tu eti moart pentru lume,  dar aa i-a fost menirea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Las gndurile triste,  maic, maic, ia psaltirea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i f-i cruce de pcat!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">....................</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Arde candela pe mas, cu o palid lumin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i bolnavele ei raze ntunericu-l ptrund.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Neclintit ca de piatr, Epifnia se-nchin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">La icoanele-nnegrite, care stau n umbra fin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe peretele din fund...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T14"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Vezi-mi inima-ntristat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Maic preacurat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i de sus mi-o lumineaz</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu cereasc raz!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">C un demon, plin de ur,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Linitea mi-o fur,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Demon ru, trimis de Domnul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S-mi alunge somnul.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">D-mi credin neclintit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pavz-n ispit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i cnd dorul m frmnt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">D-mi puteri de sfnt!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">C-mi nchin durerea ie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pentru vecinicie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i viaa mea i-o-nchin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe pmnt. Amin.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Linitea nermurit iari sufletul i-apas,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ce pustiu i ce tcere! Din bogatul ei pervaz,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Maica pururea Fecioar o privete blnd miloas,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cum st alb, nemicat, cu un cot lipit de mas</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i cu palma sub obraz.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe aceleai ci natura, oarb-n veci, pe toi ne mn,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Fr voie, tuturora ne d mrul lui Adam.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n zadar ncearc omul cu neputincioas mn</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S-i supuie mersul tainic; ea ni-e mam i stpn...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T14"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Maic, cine bate-n geam?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">......................</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4">IV</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Prin trupul ei strbate un lung fior de ghea:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">E el  i-ar vrea s cread, ca alte di, c nu e...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Un val aprins de snge i nvlete-n fa</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">ntunecndu-i mintea. Ea sare i-i descuie.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Iar el s-arat-n u ca-ntr-un pervaz de scnduri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-un clete de foc parc i-a strns inima ei.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Din noaptea minii sale, din vlmag de gnduri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Un glas adnc i strig: E nc timp de vrei!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar buzele lor arse de flacra dorinii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S-apropie n tremur i lung se mpreun.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Uitndu-i mnstirea, i cerul, i toi sfinii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ea l-a cuprins n brae cu-o patim nebun.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4">V</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Noapte-adnc i furtun,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tunetul deasupra tun</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tot mai tare: o ghiulea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Care zguduie natura,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Aruncat-n cer de-a dura</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Peste-a norilor podea.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ca sclipirile de spad</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Fulgerele-ncep s cad</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Luminnd de zeci de ori,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Jos: puternica armat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De pdure, zbuciumat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Sus: grmezile de nori...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Iar pe drum, un cal ca vntul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Bate-n goana lui pmntul.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Printre arborii uimii.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Zboar orb, ducnd pe spate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dou-umbre-mbriate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Doi amani nelegiuii...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4">VI</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Zori de ziu. Norii fug n goan mare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Un ocean de ghea rece i senin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pare ceru-n urm. Vntul bate tare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cnd din ramuri ude, tremurnd apare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Discul lunii plin.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Aurora clar i trandafirie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Rsritu-n flcri l-a aprins acum,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe cnd, prsite, reci pentru vecie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dou trupuri albe zac ntr-o pustie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Margine de drum.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i cntnd se lupt rzvrtit-armat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Lupttori de veacuri arborii gigani,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Numai luna rece  palid chip de fat </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dintr-un vrf de paltin se uit mirat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">La cei doi amani...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Crturreasa </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P49"><text:span text:style-name="T14"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Uite, ai un dar n cas,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Vorbe bune, cu temei</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De la dama cea de verde,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar s te fereti s-l iei.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pentru c nu minte cartea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ea ghicete orice gnd,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Vezi, cu dama cea de tob,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ceart, lacrimi pe curnd.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dragoste pe drum de sear</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu un crai de ghind, i</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Gnd la gnd cu bucurie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Chiar o veste vei primi...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Serioas, vistoare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu ochi negri i cumini,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">A rmas privind, copila,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Gura babei, fr dini...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T14"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cum e crai de ghind, babo?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T14"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Nalt i oache, fata mea.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T14"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">i cu ochii mari i umezi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i cam palid, nu-i aa?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Seara, cnd s se dezbrace,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Singuric n iatac,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe obrajii ei s-aprinde</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Floarea rumen de mac.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i privindu-se-n oglind</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i srut braul drept:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T14"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Crai de ghind, crai de gind,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Vin la mine, c te-atept!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Iubitei ntristate</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">A vrea un cer albastru, i pace, i lumin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ca-n basme s-mi rsar n fa o grdin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu largi crri umbrite, i flori de liliac,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i slcii plngtoare pe-o margine de lac...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Iar tu s-mi fii acolo, izvor de fericire!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu ochii mari i limpezi, cu mijlocul subire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Criasa mea iubit  regina florilor </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S-i dau o venicie de nesfrit amor!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">S nu te vd iar trist,  ci dornic de via,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu zmbetul pe buze i rumen la fa,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S uii c-ai mers odat pe-al vieii aspru drum,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T14"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">S nu te mai ajung durerile de-acum....</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Nebunul</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Am ndrgit, fr ndejde,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe zna moart  Fericirea.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S nu v batei joc de mine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Sunt om  ca voi  n toat firea...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-o vd, n fiecare noapte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Mireasa tnr cum vine;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ca o vedenie uoar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">ncet s-apropie de mine.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Din cretet, vlul alb, subire</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De-a pururi faa i-o ascunde.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Prin strvezimea lui, se vede</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Zpada formelor rotunde.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">n prul lung i negru poart</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Uscate flori de lmi...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T14"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Fiin-aievea ori prere,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Eu te iubesc de mult, zei!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar ochii ti, ascuni vederii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Nu vor, cu dulcea lor otrav,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S-mi vindece durerea-nfipt</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Adnc, n inima bolnav.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">O, vino, vino mai aproape,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Arunc vlul de pe fa!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S simt fiorul srutrii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S te cuprind odat-n brae!...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T14"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">De la-nceput i-am fost ursit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar o putere ne desparte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i ne-a menit s fim, iubite,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n veci aproape i departe.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pierdut eti pentru totdeauna,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De-mi ceri s-i dau o srutare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">C, dac m cuprinzi n brae,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ca fumul, trupul meu dispare.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">E vai de cel ce-n viaa asta,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n suflet, taina mea o poart.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cnd toi vor crede c sunt vie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">El singur tie c sunt moart!...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P53">.....................</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Plutind, pornete pe alee,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S-ascunde-n umbr de palate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i st, o clip, lng banca</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Unei perechi namorate...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">n cimitir acuma intr,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">O vd cum trece nainte:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">O artare luminoas</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pind ncet peste morminte.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-n col m-ateapt lng-o groap:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">E amgirea cea din urm...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu braele ntinse dornic,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Alerg... Puterea mi se curm...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Somnul</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cnd numai luna singur din noapte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Vegheaz din ntinderea albastr,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i cnd o raz alb, vistoare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S-a strecurat sfioas prin fereastr</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-a adormit pe pern, lng tine, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Atunci din cer, cu aripi nevzute,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Copilul morii  somnul  tainic vine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe ochii-nchii, uor s te srute...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tu, dragul meu, dac te simi prea singur</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i n-ai pe nime-n camera srac</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dect un nou duman i oaspe: foamea...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">nchide ochii! Foamea o s-i treac,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i fr veste somnul i aduce</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">O mas cu mprteti bucate, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Belugul unei lumi mai fericite,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu soare cald i parcuri, i palate...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">i nu te miri, aa firesc i pare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cnd vin din trista lor singurtate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Icoane scumpe de odinioar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Fiine dragi, de mult nmormntate.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P53">................</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">O, nger blnd, alintor durerii!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De pe cernita sufletului-zare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ridic-mi vlu-n fiecare noapte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S vd splendoarea lumii viitoare!...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Mi-aduc aminte...-n serile de iarn,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">La gura sobei,  fr s-mi dau seama,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">M cuprindeai n brae moi de visuri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cnd mi spunea poveti frumoase mama...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-acuma simt singurtatea rece</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i tot pustiul nopilor trzii.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Te chem s-mi vindeci sufletul, o clip, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar n zadar te chem,  c nu mai vii!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">O, vino iar... i s-mi aduci cu tine</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Iubitul chip de care sunt departe!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Atta am, n lumea asta mare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i rutatea lumii ne desparte...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Srut-mi ochii!  Dintre ea i mine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pieri-va ca prin farmec deprtarea:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Zmbind frumoas mi ntinde gura</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-n vis e-att de dulce srutarea...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Iubita</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe un pat de nouri vinei, adoarme luna plin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i lacul doarme-n umbr.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n adieri uoare, cnd plopii rari suspin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tresar i-ascult... Natura, din nevzute strune,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">nal ctre ceruri o lung rugciune,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i porile triei din neguri se desfac</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De vezi cum, ntre maluri cu slcii plngtoare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">A stelelor popoare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Se oglindesc n lac.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">... i dou boli cu lun acum stau fa-n fa...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Din umbra de pe maluri iubita-ncet rsare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i parc nici n-atinge pmntul pe crare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S-apropie de mine... acum mi cade-n brae...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i uit de lumea-ntreag, sorbind curatu-i suflet</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n calda, nesfrita, sublima srutare!...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Iar luna se deteapt, din nori ridic fruntea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i lung spre noi privete,  dar norii o cuprind</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n brae moi de cea, i ea, copila nopii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Adoarme iar, zmbind...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Atunci o umbr dulce se las peste fire...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Un cntec, o poveste duioas-ncepe vntul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De-o zn cu ochi limpezi i mijlocul subire...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tu, lun alb, spune-mi, de cnd priveti pmntul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ai mai vzut vrodat atta fericire?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Din prag </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ca steaua serii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">M sting n noapte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i noaptea crete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n jurul meu,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cnd tot trecutul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n suflet moare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Coboar-n urm-i</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pustiul greu...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Icoan scump</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Din alte vremuri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">mi pari acuma</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Un vis pierdut...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Vin mai aproape,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">D-mi mna alb</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i ochii negri</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S i-i srut!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Aripa morii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Arunc umbre</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe nenorocul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Celor nvini.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Strin de toate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Simt cum se las</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Genele grele</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe ochii stini...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Ctre chipul din oglind </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cum stai n ram i te uii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Att de trist la mine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">M-ntreab ochii ti mirai:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T14"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">M mai cunoti, strine?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T14"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Urtule, nu te cunosc!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Prea palid eti la fa</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i prea bolnavi ard ochii ti, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Privirea lor m-nghea...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">C te tiam copil nebun,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Crescut n vnt i soare, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Obrazul rumen, ochii vii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i gura zmbitoare.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Natura toat se-nchina,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Asculttoare ie:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Aveai palat un crng ntreg</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-o lunc-mprie!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">De-acolo, ntr-o zi, te-au dus</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">ntre strini, departe,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S uzi cu lacrimi de copil</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">O urcioas carte.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar anii lungi, ducnd cu ei</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pustiu-nvturii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">N-au stins vpaia ochilor,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Nici zmbetele gurii.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">tiai s cni i s iubeti,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pornit pe rs i glume...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar tot avntul tu pieri</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cnd ai intrat n lume.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Aa pesemne-ai fost ursit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S suferi prea devreme.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i gura ta, nici chiar acum,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Nu tie s blesteme!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P53">................</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Uor pstreaz urmele</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De pai adnci nisipul.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ci sufletul meu nu-i aa</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cum mi-l arat chipul:</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Veninul suferinelor</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n piept s mi se strng, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Eu vreau s rd!... Dar ochii ti</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Au nceput s plng.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Chemare</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">n zadar te ispitete visul vieii nestatornic!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Nu vezi tu c-n nelesul strnsului de mn dornic,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tremur belugul unei dulci comori nerisipite</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De dorini, pe care ochii nu le las tinuite?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Din pustiul pcii tale, tresrind fr s vrei,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ai rmas aa, uimit, cu privirea-n ochii mei,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar un gnd strin, deodat, i-a nmrmurit avntul </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i sfielnicele buze n-au putut opti cuvntul...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Unde i-ai lsat podoaba sufletului de fecioar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ca s tremuri naintea gndului ce te-nfioar?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Nu vezi tu c fr veste umbra serii te-a cuprins,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cnd pe cerul tu vpaia dimineii nu s-a stins </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i comoara ta de visuri vnturile-au risipit-o?...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">O, -i cunosc povestea toat, parc nsumi am trit-o.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">El i-a fost ursit pe via,  dar e-atta de strin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i de inima ta cald, i de sufletul senin!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cum s-i treac lui prin minte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S-i cuprind trupul tnr i cu vorba s te-alinte?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i aa, nedumerit, stai pe gnduri ziua-ntreag,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Nici nu-i mai aduci aminte de i-a zis vrodat: drag!...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ci ridic-te i-ascult, n a firii diminea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Glasul cntecului tnr cum te cheam la via,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tremurnd te-ateapt-un suflet s te-alinte i s-i spun</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">C nu-i moart pentru tine taina nopilor cu lun!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Vin din umbra unde floarea tinereii tale moare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Inima s i-o-nclzeasc focul razelor de soare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">D-mi-i mie ochii dornici de iubiri necunoscute,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i te-oi sruta cum nimeni n-a tiut s te srute!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">C de n-am podoabe scumpe, fericit s te slvesc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Eu am numai o avere: tiu s cnt i s iubesc!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="P66" text:outline-level="3">Noapte n ploaie </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">(Fragment dintr-un poem)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">...Mai sus, la poalele pdurii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Se-mbin umbrele-n coroan</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i ca-n poveste se deschide</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n faa noastr o poain:</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Mesteceni albi, cu ramuri goale,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe margini codrul adormit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-n raza lunii, risipite,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cpie mici de fn cosit...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Aici nu-i nimeni s ne vad</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n pacea nopii-ncremenite,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">O, farmec negrit de dulce</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Al srutrilor oprite!...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar un fior prin noapte trece.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">optesc copacii ngrozii.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Un tainic murmur,  ca o ap, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Coboar-n codrii adormii.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Vin freamte nelmurite,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Prevestitoare de furtun,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i nouri vinei, colo-n zare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Deasupra munilor s-adun...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Acum pe bolta rzvrtit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Alearg cum i poart vntul.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n valuri negre luna moare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i umbra-ntunec pmntul.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">O, doamne! Ploaia-n noaptea asta</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ne stric fr mil rostul.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar colo jos, ntr-o cpi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De fn, gsi-vom adpostul...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Stm bine-aa, sub bolta moale,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu frunile alturate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ca doi copii cumini.  Ne-mbat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Mirosul florilor uscate.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">De peste deal abia s-aude</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Un ropot repede-n pduri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">E ploaia... Pn la noi deodat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ajung rzlee picturi,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">i tot mai dese cad. Un fulger</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tria norilor despic</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Vuinid departe-n muni. Iubita</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S-a strns la pieptul meu cu fric.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Simeam atunci viaa cald</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cum tremur ca o vpaie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De foc nestins, n trupul tnr,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Sub haina umed de ploaie...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cum norii-ntunecau seninul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Nemrginirilor albastre,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">O noapte dulce-nvluise</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Lumina gndurilor noastre.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar n-a fost patim nebun</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu gnduri risipite-n oapte, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">A fost un vis frumos... i ploaia</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Curgea cu ropot lung, n noapte.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">.......................</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">.......................</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">La rsrit ncet s-aprinde</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Vpaie rece de rubin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cnd printre norii rupi s-arat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ferestre mari de cer senin.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Icoanei</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">mpins mereu ctre pcate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Un suflet trist mi-au dat prinii </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Bolnav de dorul clipei moarte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i ars de flacra dorinei.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar tu mi-ai luminat de-a pururi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Al nopilor convoi tcut,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Icoan scump,  i cu tine</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Mi-ai dus norocul n trecut.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">La tine-i caut, sfioase,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Un adpost n clipe grele,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Speranele mngietoare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i toate visurile mele...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Uoare zboar ctre tine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cum zboar fluturii uori</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Spre floarea tinuit-n umbr,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Spre cea mai dulce dintre flori...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tu, cea dinti, mi-ai dat putere</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S sfarm zgazurile minii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cnd mi-ai sdit n piept ispita,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Fiorul tainic al dorinei.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i cobornd n ochii-mi tulburi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Adnc, privirea ta de sfnt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Mi-ai dat belug de via nou</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i iubitoare mi-ai zis: cnt!...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Acum sunt singur. Eti departe,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Nepreuita mea comoar...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar vii n ceasul mut al serii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cnd linitea din cer coboar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i vd cum genele plecate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n tremur necurmat le miti,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">ntunecnd sursul gurii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu noaptea ochilor ti triti.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Zadarnic pizma altor inimi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ne-a desprit atta vreme,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">C ochii nu mai vor s plng</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i gura uit s blesteme:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Simt umbrele ce m-nconjoar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">C nu m-apas att de greu</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cnd luminezi, icoana scump,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Altarul sufletului meu...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>1908</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Domnului A. Vlahu</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Bine-ai venit, an nou!  Cu voie bun,<text:line-break/>ncreztori i-ngenunchem-nainte:<text:line-break/>Ne-aduci comoar de sperane sfinte,<text:line-break/>Ori prevestiri grozave de furtun?...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">De pretutindeni se ridic oapte<text:line-break/>i plns nbuit spre cel ce, ie,<text:line-break/>nduioat acum, i-a dat solie<text:line-break/>S luminezi odat trista noapte!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">C sunt aici dureri nemngiate,<text:line-break/>Blesteme dureroase,  sunt copii<text:line-break/>Flmnzi i goi, i casele pustii, <text:line-break/>Sunt cruci de lemn, la margine de sate...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">i morii lor ateapt de la tine,<text:line-break/>An milostiv, n toate s fii darnic <text:line-break/>i s le spui c n-au jertfit zadarnic<text:line-break/>Atta snge, gloanele haine.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">C-au ncetat slbaticele goane, <text:line-break/>Iar dac sunt colibele cernite,<text:line-break/>Copii orfani i mame vduvite<text:line-break/>Nu vor mai plnge, sara, la icoane...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:span text:style-name="T22">*</text:span><text:line-break/>Un glas pornit din inim curat,<text:line-break/>Un tnr glas te-ntmpin acum:<text:line-break/>Din largul rii spulber odat<text:line-break/>Mirosul greu de snge i de fum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">An nou, an sfnt,  adu belug n ar!<text:line-break/>Dar s nu lege-n ern sngerat<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Un rod spurcat, smna cea bogat...<text:line-break/> An sfnt, adu-ni alt primvar!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">S-nfrni, cu grija zilelor de mine,<text:line-break/>Nelegiuitul rs al lcomiei <text:line-break/>i din prinosul roadelor cmpiei<text:line-break/>S se hrneasc cei ce ne dau pine.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">De fructe multe, pomii ncrcai<text:line-break/>i spicul greu de boabe s se rup!<text:line-break/>O, an frumos,  cu bogii astup<text:line-break/>Prpastia deschis ntre frai!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">mpac vrajba sufletelor noastre!<text:line-break/>Nici plnsu-amar, nici blestemele gurii,<text:line-break/>Nici pumnii strni de vechiul foc al urii<text:line-break/>S n-amenine cerurile-albastre...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Te-om preamri n laude, cu toii,<text:line-break/>O, an al pcii binefctoare!<text:line-break/>i-i vor aduce-n veacuri viitoare<text:line-break/>Prinosul lor de cinste, strnepoii!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">n taina nopii </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe crare, lng codru,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Numai pasul meu s-aude...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ploaia picur din frunze</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i din ramurile ude.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Norii-ntunecai mbrac</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cerul nopii fr stele, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Luminoi mi-arat calea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Numai ochii dragii mele!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Du-m, dorule, cu tine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Toat jalea s mi-o-ngropi </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pn&apos; la casa tinuit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Casa alb dintre plopi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P53"><text:soft-page-break/>................</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dulce clip a-ntlnirii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Mintea-ntreag mi-o rpeti!...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">...Dar nu-i nime-n prisp-afar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Nici lumin la fereti!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">...............</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="P66" text:outline-level="3">nserarea </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">(Fragment dintr-un poem)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dup culmi de piatr sur cnd i pleac-ncet mrirea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Soarele srut codrii unde doarme mnstirea.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">ntre brazi ferii de vnturi, lng zid de stnc drept,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">A durat-o-n vremuri grele domn viteaz i nelept.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Sus, la turla care-apas bolt grea de crmid,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe o lespede umbrit n privazul de firid,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Slova veche, ocrotit de al vremii sfnt Visternic,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Spune leatul i domnia voievodului cucernic.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Umbra lui vegheaz parc din btrnele chilii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Prin despictura neagr a ferestrelor pustii...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar acum ncremenit poarta schitului rmne,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cnd coboar seara, nimeni n-o mai mic din ne.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Vremea-i macin cu-ncetul putregaiul sub zbrele,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe veriga ruginit nu mai cad lacte grele, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ci prielnic duhul pcii stpnete-aici de veacuri...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Iar pe stlpi cu zugrveal, din naltele cerdacuri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ca un semn de biruin rde vesel-n culori</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Minunata strlucire a belugului de flori.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-n amurgul serii calde munii Coziei s-arat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cum i zugrvesc pe ceruri muchea neagr i crestat, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tot mai roii scad n zare luminoasele vpi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Vlul nopii se coboar tot mai negru peste vi...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>mpcare</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tovar scump de clipe grele</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Am vrut s-mi fii pe drumul greu:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-am dat ndejdea vieii mele,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Un cer senin cu mndre stele </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i floarea sufletului meu.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar floarea, cnd ai vrut s-o scuturi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S-a vetejit n mna ta.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Acu-n zadar mi ceri sruturi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Alearg iar: vei prinde fluturi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i ali obraji vei sruta!...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Nu-i mai ceresc, ca-n alt vreme,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">ngenuncheat sursul tu.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">O, nu,  cu tainice blesteme,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Din calea ta n-or s te cheme</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Nici lacrimi, nici preri de ru.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">A mea a fost cea mai frumoas</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Din partea minunatei pini;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De restul ei nimic nu-mi pas:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Adun restul de pe mas</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-arunc-l, draga mea, la cni!...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe tine, cea de altdat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Lumin stins pentru veci,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Aa cum visul meu te-arat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Eu te iubesc... Dar niciodat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe tine, umbr care pleci!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">De-aceea, mpcat cu mine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n urma ta, strin m vezi.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Nu-i zic dect: te du cu bine!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">..........................</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i zmbitor m uit la tine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cum tot mai mult te deprtezi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Vecina</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">M ceri mereu, dar nu sunt eu de vin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ci numai ochii,  ochii ti, vecin, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">C i-am fcut potec prin grdin...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Adeseori tu lai la geamuri storul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i ua ta e-nchis cu zvorul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar tot mai viu s-aprinde-n mine dorul!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">i tot mai des m poart necuratul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Spre zmbetul din ochii ti, cu sfatul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe care-l in ispita i pcatul.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">De dorul tu, de dragul suferinei,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cnd amgit mi-oi pierde rostul minii, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tu vrei s-mi las i fraii, i prinii?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">S leg acum ce nu se mai dezleag,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S ispesc viaa mea ntreag</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pcatul greu c mi-eti att de drag?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dect s fug cu tine-n larg lume,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ori singur eu, s nu-i mai tiu de nume, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Mai bine-mpac-mi dragostea cu glume.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Zmbind s-mi vindeci inima rnit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pstreaz calda ochilor ispit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar nu mai ine ua zvort!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">C tu i-nconjuri viaa cu zvoare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i clipele de-acum le lai s zboare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cnd duclea tineree-i trectoare...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">De ce nu vrei s lai n prag vemntul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De datini grele ce-mi ucid avntul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">C nu ne-ar ti nici vntul, nici pmntul!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cnd umbra nopii cade peste vale,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tu s m-atepi n pragul casei tale,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">C-un vl uor pe umerele goale.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">S vin, cnd luna nopilor miestre,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Frumoas ca o fat fr zestre, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Se uit lung i tainic prin ferestre...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Clipe de zbucium </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Iubita mea, te simt aa departe...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Mi-ai pus pe frumte minile subiri, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar, ca un zid puternic, ne desparte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">O pnz de cernite amintiri.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Fiina mea ntreag cnd te cere,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tu stai visnd, nici ochii nu i-i miti, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i cte taine pline de durere</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Se pierd n noaptea ochilor ti triti!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Eu chem osnda care m omoar, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Slbatic vntul patimii s bat, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Eu cer icoana ta de-odinioar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe care n-am vzut-o niciodat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">O, cum a vrea durerea s mi-o-nele!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Attea nopi pustii am adorat-o,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">I-am dat i jertfa tinereii mele</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Zmbind... Tu numai inima mi-ai dat-o.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Mi-ai dat-o! Floare ginga de munte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ce st deasupra unui larg abis...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">(i chiar acum, cnd m srui pe frunte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tu m srui cum se srut-n vis!)</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cci sufletul, ca tristele ruine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pstreaz-n el lumina altor vremuri, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i cnd o raz-ajunge pn&apos; la mine</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Atunci te simt, iubita mea, cum tremuri:</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ea lumineaz-n tine, fr veste,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Prpastia trecutului ntreg...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-atunci duioasa inimii poveste</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Eu o ascult,  dar n-o mai neleg.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P53">........................</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">De-aceea-n sara asta mi-e totuna,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Sporete-mi iar durerea sau alin-o,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Te-ntreb,  pierdut pentru totdeauna: </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De unde vii i cine eti, strino?...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Pruncul</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Un vl de cea alb i subire,<text:line-break/>Ca un linoliu strveziu de mort,<text:line-break/>nconjura biserica btrn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">i-n dimineaa zilei de aprile<text:line-break/>Simeai plutind n aer, pretundindeni,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Fiori, adnci fiori de fericire, <text:line-break/>Prinosul larg al firii, cnd pmntul<text:line-break/>n mii de forme druie luminii<text:line-break/>Belugul lui puternic de via...<text:line-break/>Pluteau spre cer miresme-ngemnate<text:line-break/>Cci liliacul tnr nflorise<text:line-break/>i crengi plecate ascundeau n umbr<text:line-break/>Mnunchiuri de sfioase viorele.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">i-n dimineaa zilei de aprile<text:line-break/>Vedeai cum st ncremenit gloat<text:line-break/>De muncitori i de femei tcute<text:line-break/>Pe treptele amvonului pustiu.<text:line-break/>Iar colo, jos, pe-o lespede de piatr,<text:line-break/>n faa lor sta pruncul prsit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Un pumn de rn, o scnteie rupt<text:line-break/>Din flacra etern a vieii...<text:line-break/>i trupul cald topise bruma nopii<text:line-break/>Ce se-nchega n picturi curate<text:line-break/>Ca nite lacrimi reci de muceni<text:line-break/>Sclipind pe faa lespezilor aspre.<text:line-break/>Prea c piatra neclintit plnge!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Cum se strngea, nfiorat de frig,<text:line-break/>Plpndul trup ursit de-acum durerii,<text:line-break/>i faa-i mic s-o cuprinzi n palm,<text:line-break/>Cum ntindea guria dup hran,<text:line-break/>Cu buzele-i att de diafane<text:line-break/>Ca dou foi subiri de trandafir!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Cum, printre voi, nu-i nimeni,  nici o mam<text:line-break/>S-i smulg-acum vemntul de la sn?...<text:line-break/>O, ascultai micuul glas cum plnge.<text:line-break/>Cum cere pruncul partea lui de soare!<text:line-break/>Dar unde eti, s-l vezi acum, pierduto,<text:line-break/>Femeie, tu, de trei ori blestemat!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:soft-page-break/>Te-o blestema bastardul fr nume,<text:line-break/>Nevinovatul osndit s moar<text:line-break/>Cnd nimnuia n-a cerut via, <text:line-break/>i cnd ntiul vnt de patimi grele,<text:line-break/>Din lumea rea, porni-va s-l doboare,<text:line-break/>Te-o blestema copilul trist i palid<text:line-break/>C n-are cui opti, cu lacrimi: mam!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Te-i blestema tu singur odat,<text:line-break/>Ducnd povara vechiului pcat,<text:line-break/>Zadarnic vei ntinde dup sprijin<text:line-break/>Tremurtoare brae istovite, <text:line-break/>i pnza neagr-a gndurilor tale<text:line-break/>Cerni-va golul nopilor trzii,<text:line-break/>C nu-i avea nici trista mngiere<text:line-break/>S gemi plngnd: aveam flcu acum!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">De ce nu vii s i-l ridici n brae?...<text:line-break/>Cu mnile de munc sngerate,<text:line-break/>S curmi rna i s-i caui hran,<text:line-break/>Rznd s lupi,  s plngi nvingtoare,<text:line-break/>S-nfruni apoi dispreul tuturora,<text:line-break/>Nevrednicul dispre al celor slabi, <text:line-break/>i mndr, cu privirile senine,<text:line-break/>Punnd un bra pe umru-i puternic,<text:line-break/>Tu s-l ari atuncea lumii-ntregi:<text:line-break/>Copilul meu,  al meu -al nimnui!...</text:p>
   <text:list xml:id="list8451828" text:style-name="L24">
    <text:list-header>
     <text:p text:style-name="P96">*</text:p>
     <text:p text:style-name="P109">Dar iat,  gloata-ncet se risipete...<text:line-break/>Posomort, n vinete veminte<text:line-break/>Un om s-apleac i ridic pruncul, <text:line-break/>Apoi cu paii rari i grei se duce...</text:p>
    </text:list-header>
   </text:list>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Iar soarele, nsngernd altarul,<text:line-break/>Se ridic din ceaa dimineii<text:line-break/>i razele, sclipind tremurtoare,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cdeau pe faa zidurilor aspre,<text:line-break/>n dimineaa zilei de aprile,<text:line-break/>Cdeau ca pe-o ruin...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Taina nopii </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">n lumina lunii doarme</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Casa dragii mele,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">I-au cuprins pridvorul tainic</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ramuri de zorele.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dulci chemri nelmurite</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tremur departe.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Draga mea a dat sfioas</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Crengile-ntr-o parte.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">i pridvorul parc-ateapt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Oaspele grdinii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar m bate luna-n fa</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i m tiu vecinii...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T14"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Lun alb, lun mut,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Lun cltoare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cum te-a smulge de pe ceruri</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S te-arunc n mare!...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Epitafuri</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">pe mormntul:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P62">Unui beiv</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">De srcie i necaz<text:line-break/>ntia oar doarme treaz.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P62">Unui so iubit</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Ici doarme Ni Busuioc, <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i nu mai sforie deloc!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P62">Unui vardist</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Ce te-ai oprit la criptolog?<text:line-break/>Hai, circulai, m rog!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P62">Unui prost</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">El doarme eapn, doarme drept, <text:line-break/>Dar tii voi: cnd a fost detept?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P62">Lui A. C. Cuza</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Hei, trectorule, -napoi!<text:line-break/>...S nu-i miroi a usturoi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P62">Iubitei</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">S-a stins. Dar s n-o plngi, strine,<text:line-break/>Mai mult pe ea dect pe mine!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cntec</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-mi fcui din doruri mute</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cntece nepricepute, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i din cntecele mele</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Salb de mrgele.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Inim cu dulce chin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cine m-a-ndemnat s-anin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dup gtul dragii mele</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Salba de mrgele?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">C le smulse fr vin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S le risipeasc-n tin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Roii boabe de mrgele,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dorurile mele!...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Fata trist </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Firul gndului frumos</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Un suspin mi-l taie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">C de-atta vreme cos</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Singur-n odaie.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">i doar mna mea, cu greu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Flori de fir mparte.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Flori aleg,  dar gndul meu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Gndul mi-e departe!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Uneori, cnd in la piept</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Strns custura,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">nchid ochii i-l atept</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S-mi srute gura.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Iar cnd umbra serii vine</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dorul crete-n mine</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i tristeea m doboar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Grea, ca o povar...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">O, tiu bine c-n zadar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dragostea m mn</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S-l atept cu lacrimi iar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Nopatea, la fntn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Nu mai vine s-i optesc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dorurile toate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i la sn s-i nclzesc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Minile-ngheate!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ci doar vntul nopii rece</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Fruntea mi-o srut,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Peste codri luna trece</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Galben i mut.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Lung suspin-n freamt greu</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Fagii de pe coaste...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Noapte dulce, dragul meu</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">A plecat n oaste.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Ceasornicului meu</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ce,  iar ai aipit?... Ruine<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>C pori blazonul de patent!<text:line-break/>Te iu, de-o lun, eu pe tine<text:line-break/>Cu mersul vremii n curent.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Mainria ta perfect<text:line-break/>Cunoate ordinul legal<text:line-break/>i-n fiecare zi respect<text:line-break/>Repaosul... duminical.</text:p>
   <text:list xml:id="list674085207" text:style-name="L25">
    <text:list-header>
     <text:p text:style-name="P97">*</text:p>
     <text:p text:style-name="P110">Dar poate lai necontrolate<text:line-break/>S curg clipele n haos, <text:line-break/>C ai i tu nevoie, frate,<text:line-break/>De linite i de repaos.</text:p>
    </text:list-header>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P110">Eti surmenat i tu pesemne<text:line-break/>Ca i stpnu-tu, sracul!<text:line-break/>Ce lege poate s te-ndemne<text:line-break/>S bai necontenit tic-tacul?...</text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P110">Eti atacat, cu siguran.<text:line-break/>Deci, ct vreme pulsu-i bate,<text:line-break/>Te duc la munte pe vacan, <text:line-break/>...La muntele de pietate.</text:p>
    </text:list-item>
   </text:list>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Eclips</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe-aceleai ci de mii de ani umblate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n goluri vaste legnndu-i sfera,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Neptun ador vistor pe Terra, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">O biat lume plin de pcate...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">El niciodat n-a trecut bariera</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Singurtii lui nevinovate, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-n clipa asta ea e moart, poate:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">O umbr deas-i umple atmosfera.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Neptun, se vede c tu n-ai lunet</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S-i studiezi eclipsa de departe, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cnd inocenta tnr planet</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Se-ntreab, cu privirea-ntr-alt parte:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ce face oare Venera cochet</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe ntuneric, singur cu Marte?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Doleanele unui cronicar teatral</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Pe cerul plin de sclipitoare puncte,<text:line-break/>Trec efemere linii de lumin.<text:line-break/>Sub pasul meu ntrziat, suspin<text:line-break/>Sonorul glas al frunzelor defuncte.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Zadarnic luna m petrece-n cale<text:line-break/>Pe bulevardul alb i singuratic, <text:line-break/>C subsemnatul, cronicar dramatic,<text:line-break/>Acum e-n rolul misiunii sale.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">De-abia ncerc un singur vers de od, <text:line-break/>i-n capul meu vin stafii inedite,<text:line-break/>Cu gesturi largi,  cu rcnete cumplite:<text:line-break/>Mooc, Spancioc, Ciubr i Despot-vod!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Sunt eu?... Sunt treaz?... Deschide-te, morminte!...<text:line-break/>Deodat tace ritmicul meu pas:<text:line-break/>n scena a III-a, mi-am adus aminte,<text:line-break/>Madam Pruteanu a strmbat din nas.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">De ce-a strmbat?... Probabil, o nuan<text:line-break/>De fin dispre, cnd vede pe Carmina, <text:line-break/>Fiindc-i pierde ultima speran...<text:line-break/>De n-a uita nuana cu pricina!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">i iar pornesc... dar m opresc deodat.<text:line-break/>Ah, sunt dator s fiu cu mintea-n patru:<text:line-break/>De ce nu vin ieenii toi la teatru?...<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>O chestiune foarte complicat!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Francisca... art... rasa i talentul...<text:line-break/>Deci, vaszic, vor s se rzbune...<text:line-break/>Ce-i vinovat Onor. Direciune?<text:line-break/>Domnia-sa regret incidentul...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">...Vr degetul n buzunarul vestii,<text:line-break/>Sunt plictisit i-mi pare ru de lun.<text:line-break/>Hm!... bulevardul pare o lagun...<text:line-break/>Mi-e capul plin cu fel de fel de chestii.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Dar e-n zadar!...<text:line-break/>Va trebui s scriu<text:line-break/>(Chiar dac-ar fi s nu mai cnt o lun)<text:line-break/>De Dragomir, de pies  c e bun.<text:line-break/>De Toma, de Pisoschi, tot ce tiu!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">...A ataca pe d. Sadoveanu<text:line-break/>(Cci n-a aniversat pe d. Iorga),<text:line-break/>A luda pe d-ra Horga,<text:line-break/>Dar ce-o s zic d. Ibrileanu?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Chiar dac-n Ilia a fost perfect,<text:line-break/>O s v par c... mi s-a prut!<text:line-break/>(Dealtminteri, eu tiam de la-nceput<text:line-break/>C voi emite-o laud suspect...)</text:p>
   <text:list xml:id="list1021802039" text:style-name="L26">
    <text:list-header>
     <text:p text:style-name="P101">*</text:p>
    </text:list-header>
   </text:list>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Aa, m duc ursuz prin promoroac,<text:line-break/>n pacea nopii albe i compacte, <text:line-break/>i nici nu tiu c-n capul meu se joac<text:line-break/>O tragedie-n paisprezece acte!...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>De profundis</text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4">I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Nu, asta nu pot s-o suport!<text:line-break/>Curnd, e-un an i jumtate<text:line-break/>De cnd ai declarat c-s mort<text:line-break/>n unanimitate.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Toi protii ci m-au cunoscut<text:line-break/>Ziceau: Mi-era un fel de rud <text:line-break/>Sracul! Cine-ar fi crezut?...<text:line-break/>mi vine s-nviez de ciud!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Profane mini mi-au rsfoit,<text:line-break/>La Iai, arhiva.<text:line-break/>Revistele m-au prohodit,<text:line-break/>Amicii mi-au mncat coliva.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">M pipi, stau nedumerit.<text:line-break/>M trag de pr, simt c m doare...<text:line-break/>Nu, n-am murit!<text:line-break/>V dau cuvntul de onoare.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Scriu versuri proaste, deci exist!<text:line-break/>Mi-e dor, mi-e foarte dor de-o fat.<text:line-break/>Triesc, de vreme ce sunt trist<text:line-break/>i rd ca altdat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Dar astzi, negru i zburlit<text:line-break/>De cum m-a prins dumanul, <text:line-break/>V dau de veste c-am sosit<text:line-break/>ntreg, i eu, i geamantanul!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:soft-page-break/>II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Am fost la nceput n rai<text:line-break/>La Neam, la mnstire:<text:line-break/>Pduri de cetini, flori de plai,<text:line-break/>Singurtate i iubire...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Pe urm am intrat n iad<text:line-break/>La Turtucaia,<text:line-break/>i nc miroseam a brad<text:line-break/>Cnd s-a-nceput btaia.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Acolo jos, un cpitan<text:line-break/>Cu barba rar<text:line-break/>M-a pus alturi d-un igan<text:line-break/>S-mi dau viaa pentru ar.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Mi se prea c e un basm,<text:line-break/>Cnd gloanele veneau din vale<text:line-break/>Spre mine, cu entuziasm<text:line-break/>i cu intenii criminale.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">M cutau prin cucuruz<text:line-break/>S m mnnce, s m frig!<text:line-break/>i cnd cdea cte-un obuz<text:line-break/>Ct un ceaun de mmlig,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Trosnea, cu flacr i fum,<text:line-break/>De se cutremura maidanul, <text:line-break/>nct m minunez -acum<text:line-break/>C nu mi-au spart timpanul!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">De-acuma chiar de m-a zvrli<text:line-break/>ntr-o vultoare,<text:line-break/>De mine Moartea va fugi<text:line-break/>Cu coasa-ntre picioare.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Cci i va zice-n gndul ei:<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Mor toi,  flmndul i stulul...<text:line-break/>Dar sta are obicei<text:line-break/>S-mi trag chiulul!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Pota redaciei </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Citete-mi oda i repet-o,<text:line-break/>Amicul meu necunoscut.<text:line-break/>Tu, colaborator in petto,<text:line-break/>Primete primul meu salut!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">De cum ncepe s vorbeasc<text:line-break/>Romnul nostru e poet.<text:line-break/>Nu-i om n ara romneasc<text:line-break/>S nu fi scris un triolet,<text:line-break/>O strof p-un album de fat<text:line-break/>Sau cel puin un acrosti<text:line-break/>Pe care, tremurnd, odat,<text:line-break/>L-a dat iubitei pe furi...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">De-aceea fr suprare<text:line-break/>Noi i ntindem mna, frate:<text:line-break/>A tale crime literare<text:line-break/>Mai dinainte-i sunt iertate...<text:line-break/>De vrei s publici versuri nule,<text:line-break/>Vreo nuvelet, un articol, <text:line-break/>Noi am luat msuri destule<text:line-break/>S te scpm de-acest pericol.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Consemnul nostru e teribil:<text:line-break/>S-aduci nti certificat<text:line-break/>Precum c eti inamovibil, <text:line-break/>Profesor... pop... magistrat...<text:line-break/>S-i faci nti o carier,<text:line-break/>Ori cel puin o sinecur,<text:line-break/>Ceva, un loc n atmosfer...<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i mai apoi literatur.<text:line-break/>Credeam i noi odinioar<text:line-break/>i poate astzi credem nc,<text:line-break/>Dei iluziile zboar, <text:line-break/>C tot ce zboar se mnnc...<text:line-break/>Da, zboar gndurile mele<text:line-break/>i versul meu e-naripat, <text:line-break/>i-n loc s mnnc eu din ele,<text:line-break/>Pe mine ele m-au mncat!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P23">*</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Dar dac simi arznd n tine<text:line-break/>Al artei foc nepotolit,<text:line-break/>Cldura flcrii divine<text:line-break/>Ce i pe mine m-au prlit;<text:line-break/>De vrei ca vulgul s te-admire<text:line-break/>i orice prost impertinent<text:line-break/>C-un zmbet de comptimire<text:line-break/>S-i zic: bravo, ai talent!<text:line-break/>n existena ta pribeag<text:line-break/>Tot singur, mndru i srac,<text:line-break/>De vrei s lupi cu lumea-ntreag<text:line-break/>Ca Cyrano de Bergerac;<text:line-break/>De-s n zadar a mele sfaturi</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Pe lng visul tu, frumos<text:line-break/>Ca un castel cu zece caturi<text:line-break/>Din care cazi cu capu-n jos;<text:line-break/>De vrei s fii trimis n frunte<text:line-break/>Cnd s-o isca un nou rzboi,<text:line-break/>i nenorocul s te-nfrunte<text:line-break/>Cnd te-i ntoarce napoi, <text:line-break/>Necazuri cu nemiluita<text:line-break/>n lunga ta captivitate,<text:line-break/>S-i pierzi amicii i iubita<text:line-break/>-un post la Universitate...<text:line-break/>Visnd, n urm, o balad<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cu muni, cu soare, i cu flori,<text:line-break/>S tragi pe Lucifer de coad<text:line-break/>Precum l-ai tras de-attea ori;<text:line-break/>i dac vrei s ai, pe lng<text:line-break/>Acestea, -alte mici belele:<text:line-break/>De vrei ca gheata s te strng<text:line-break/>i ca iubita s te-nele,<text:line-break/>Flirtnd cu primul ntflea<text:line-break/>Pe care-l are la-ndemn,<text:line-break/>-apoi din nou s-i cad-n brae<text:line-break/>De apte ori pe sptmn;<text:line-break/>De vrei ca dup astea toate<text:line-break/>De-a binele s-nnebuneti,<text:line-break/>C-o hain verde roas-n coate<text:line-break/>i cu jambiere muscleti;<text:line-break/>Cnd i-ai pierdut complet busola<text:line-break/>S faci bucluc dup bucluc,<text:line-break/>De vrei s intri la Socola,<text:line-break/>S scapi de-atta balamuc,<text:line-break/>Ori s-i fii victim i gde<text:line-break/>Tu ie singur deopotriv...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">i dac totui i surde<text:line-break/>Aceast neagr perspectiv,<text:line-break/>Ia pana, domnul meu, i... scrie!<text:line-break/>Eu unul nu pot s te scap.<text:line-break/>Dar te previu, ca s se tie,<text:line-break/>C singur i-ai fcut de cap.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Scrisori iubite </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Scrisori pstrate de demult...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">n linitit zi cu soare, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu fruntea-n mini m plec s-ascult</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tcerea voastr vorbitoare.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ce fericit eram odat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i ct sunt ostenit de drum!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar ea,  pe unde-o fi acum?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ce s-a fcut frumoasa fat?...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">C ne-am iubit ca doi nebuni,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Iar astzi nu mai am n fa</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dect un maldr de minciuni</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Legate cu un fir de a.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Catrene improvizate </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P61">(n onoarea ilustrului Tsloanu)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ca o comet fr coad</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ai aprut pe firmament</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu-al tu Luceafr pus pe sfad, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar n-ai talent.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ai tot ce-i trebuie: hrtie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cerneal, public indulgent,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Parale i tipografie, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar n-ai talent.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Te-ai instalat n Capital</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ca s creezi i tu curent.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Vrei s te-afirmi ca cap de coal, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar n-ai talent.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">La cafenea cnd vii alene</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i iei un aer grav, absent...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Satisfcut te umfli-n pene, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar n-ai talent.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Iar cnd te duci s scrii acas</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Un nou articol vehement,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Te strmbi urt, te-aezi la mas...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar n-ai talent.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Avntul tu i idealul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Plasat n ar cu procent</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i salt-ntruna capitalul, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar n-ai talent.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Constai de dou ori pe lun</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">C-i d bilanul excedent.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Negustoria merge strun, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar n-ai talent!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Eti fr scrupul i msur</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cnd vrei s scapi de-un concurent.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i fierbe sufletul de ur, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar n-ai talent.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Nu ne distruge dintr-o dat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Catone, fii mai indulgent!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tu ai o mutr indignat, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar n-ai talent...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Portret</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ea are ochii mari,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ea are gura mic,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Un corp cu forme tari</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i graii de pisic.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dorine, pururi noi </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Scntei ascunse-n vatr </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i dou brae moi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-o inim de piatr.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">oapte</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P49"><text:span text:style-name="T6">n noaptea trist care ne desparte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tu poate simi n jurul tu suspine</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i flfiri de aripi i de oapte...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">E dorul meu ce vine de departe</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i ostenit adoarme lng tine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cuminte ca un fluture de noapte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ce s-a lsat la capul tu, pe-o carte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">nchis de la sine</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cnd ai simit c somnul ne desparte...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Fables microscopiques</text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4">Toto et lauto </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"> Au revoir! dit Toto<text:line-break/>Et partit en auto.<text:line-break/>Il navait nul souci.<text:line-break/>Au tournant dangereux<text:line-break/>Il lui crva un pneu...<text:line-break/>Toto crva aussi.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T27"><text:tab/></text:span>Moralit:<text:line-break/>Mourir cest partir un peu...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4">Le vaillant moucheron </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Un moucheron d&apos;un jour piqua le grand Ene...<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T27"><text:tab/></text:span>Moralit:<text:line-break/>La valeur n&apos;attend pas le nombre des annes!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4">Fable esquimaude </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Un grand ours blanc mangea un petit daim.<text:line-break/>Il assouvit sa faim<text:line-break/>Au moins pour une fois...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:span text:style-name="T23">Moralit:</text:span><text:line-break/>On a toujours besoin d&apos;un plus petit que soi.</text:p>
   <text:section text:style-name="Sect1" text:name="toc">
    <text:h text:style-name="P57" text:outline-level="4">Lne philosophe</text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Un jeune ne amoureux d&apos;une noble cavale,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Lui demanda la main (le sabot de devant).</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T14"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">Mais... vous tes du peuple, et moi  je suis pur sang,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Je vous ferai cocu! lui promit-elle.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T14"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">J&apos;avale</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tout ce que vous voudrez! dit l&apos;ne sans moi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Car...</text:span></text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T11">Moralit:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Promettre c&apos;est noble, tenir serait bourgeois...</text:span></text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Lumin</text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Viseaz plopul, nemicat n soare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i umbra din el, neagr, i curge la picioare...</text:span></text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Un melc i taie drumul prin grdin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De-a dreptul, ca un tanc de gelatin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ameninnd albine i furnici</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu patru tunuri mici.</text:span></text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Tcerea i adun trupul sferic</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">ntr-un boboc de nalb.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">O musc trece prin lumina alb,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ca o scnteie de-ntuneric,</text:span></text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Un fluture, cu aripi de umbr i mtas</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Stropite-n dou locuri cu carmin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Din zboru-i frnt i plutitor se las</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe vrful unui spin.</text:span></text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">i florile se-nal-ntr-un picior</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S-l poat contempla mai bine.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cum doarme-n pragul clipei care vine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu aripile desfcute-n viitor.</text:span></text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Acuarel</text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">n pdurea de cristal</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ca un alb decor de teatru,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Stau copacii vertical</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">(Trei plus douzeci i patru).</text:span></text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">nger trist de abanos,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">nger mic</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">S-a trezit cu faa-n jos</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">ntr-un cuib de borangic.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Un luceafr ideal,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Verde i s-a prins pe gene,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ca un fulg de papagal</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Din pduri braziliene.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Iar cpunii de pe jos</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i trimit n nri mireazm</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De tmie i aghiazm,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pruncului de abanos.</text:span></text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Paragini...</text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="P49"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe-aici,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">A fost pmntul binecuvntat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De trei vldici</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i de-un mitropolit primat.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">A fost odinioar i-un castel</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu bru multicolor de portolac.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-n fundul parcului, un lac</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu nuferi de argint pe luciu de oel.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">A fost...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Acum, abia se mai cunoate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">O balt prsit, la o parte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Singurtatea strig din apele ei moarte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Spre cer, cu glas de broate.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i numai calul-dracului,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Prin linitea srac dimprejur,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Atinge faa lacului</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cu aripi de azur.</text:span></text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Biografie</text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="P61">(Replic)</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">A fost un om ca orice om de treab</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ca tine i ca mine bunoar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i care niciodat nu se-ntreab</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ce interes au oamenii s moar.</text:span></text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Aa, fiindc s-a trezit pe lume</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ca omul care n-a cerut anume,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">El i-a fcut n atmosfer loc,</text:span></text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i-a-nfipt n vnt cciula uguiat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">i s-a-ncrustat n spaiu ca un bloc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">De piatr detunat.</text:span></text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">Dar ntr-o zi, cscnd prea tare gura,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Pe veci i-a-ncremenit fptura.</text:span></text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T6">i sufletul nchis n el, sracul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Spre cer a dat nval,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Ca ntunericul dintr-o cutie goal</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Cnd ai deschis capacul.</text:span></text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Martie</text:h>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4">Singurtate</text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Prin luminiul crngului tcut,<text:line-break/>De-atta vreme nimeni n-a trecut.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Copacii goi, n lung nemicare,<text:line-break/>Pe umbra lor ce st-nlat n picioare.<text:line-break/>Arar ajunge pn-aici<text:line-break/>O pasre cu aripile mici,<text:line-break/>i glasul ei rsun n linite prea tare.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dar Primvara, care tie tot,<text:line-break/>Va risipi prin iarba dimprejur<text:line-break/>Scntei de-azur <text:line-break/>Albastru miozot.<text:line-break/>i dintre foi tivite cu argint,<text:line-break/>Vor crete ciucuri albi de mrgrint.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">*</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Pe-aici, o zn mic coboar dintre stele,<text:line-break/>i-n fiecare noapte culege viorele.<text:line-break/>Dar nimnui pe lume nu-i e dat s-o vad<text:line-break/>Cum vine pe crrile din mlad,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Fcnd n tain ndelung popas,<text:line-break/>Din loc n loc, pe unde-a mai rmas<text:line-break/>Zpad...</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4">Vin igncile la crng... </text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Vin igncile la crng<text:line-break/>S culeag viorele,<text:line-break/>Vin cu fustele-n parng<text:line-break/>i cu dancii dup ele.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">i e soare<text:line-break/>Pe ponoare,<text:line-break/>i miroase-n vnt a floare<text:line-break/>Pe crrile pustii,</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Prin stufiurile goale<text:line-break/>Npdite de basmale<text:line-break/>i de zdrene stacojii...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Vin igncile grbit,<text:line-break/>S culeag pe sub mlad<text:line-break/>Flori cu mzg de zpad<text:line-break/>Din huceagul adormit,<text:line-break/>i s-aduc-n panera<text:line-break/>Primvara la ora:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg"> Urzicle, urzicle,<text:line-break/>Ghiocei i viorele,<text:line-break/>Albstrie de suhat!<text:line-break/> Iarb-mare, iarb-mare,<text:line-break/>S i-o puie-n scldtoare<text:line-break/>Fetele de mritat...</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Aprilie</text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Baloane mari de spum alb prin grdini<text:line-break/>(i zarzrul, i viinul, i perii)<text:line-break/>Stau gata s se-nale din tulpini<text:line-break/>Spre cerul primverii...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Caisul nostru s-a gtit la poart<text:line-break/>Cu panglici albe, ca-n tablouri vechi,<text:line-break/>i cu zulufi de floare la urechi,<text:line-break/>Cum astzi nicieri nu se mai poart.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Pe strada mare,<text:line-break/>Ies flori nalte la plimbare<text:line-break/>n rochii de sezon, uoare,<text:line-break/>Cu toate c-i o vreme aa de schimbtoare.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ah, fetele  i mai ales cucoanele <text:line-break/>Cnd vine primvara<text:line-break/>Sunt dulci i colorate ca bomboanele!</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Pe cea care-a trecut o cheam Clara,<text:line-break/>Fiindc are<text:line-break/>Ochi albatri tare,<text:line-break/>i gura ei cu rouge ca de coral<text:line-break/>Surde vertical...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Un mic vrtej, copil al Nefiinei,<text:line-break/>De-a curmeziul strzii rtcit,<text:line-break/>Nebun n jurul lui s-a rsucit<text:line-break/>S-i prind coada galben cu dinii.<text:line-break/>Departe, n azurul dintre nori,<text:line-break/>S-arat bifurcat pe cer<text:line-break/>Un ir subire de cocori,<text:line-break/>O escadril de pe vremea lui Homer...</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Ci ca voi! </text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Sus, pe gardul dinspre vie,<text:line-break/>O gin cenuie<text:line-break/>i-un coco mpintenat<text:line-break/>S-au suit i stau la sfat:<text:line-break/> Ia te uit, m rog ie,<text:line-break/>Ct de sus ne-am nlat!...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">i deodat, cu glas mare,<text:line-break/>ncepur amndoi,<text:line-break/>S cotcodceasc-n soare:<text:line-break/> Nimeni-nu-mai-e-ca-noi!...<text:line-break/>Nimeni-nu-mai-e-ca-noi!...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dar de sus, din corcodu,<text:line-break/>Pitulndu-se-ntre foi,<text:line-break/>Mititel i jucu,<text:line-break/>Le-a rspuns un piigoi:<text:line-break/> Ci-ca-voi! Ci-ca-voi!...</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Iepurele</text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Vine iarna de la munte,<text:line-break/>Peste ape face punte<text:line-break/>i pe cmp fr hotar<text:line-break/>Parc presur zahar.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Uite, colo, mo Vasile,<text:line-break/>C-un cojoc de zece chile<text:line-break/>i cu flinta la spinare<text:line-break/>A ieit la vntoare.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dintr-un codru, din tufi,<text:line-break/>Iese-un iepure furi<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i cum scap pe crare...<text:line-break/>Fuge ca o artare...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Flinta face bum! iar mou<text:line-break/>St i-i freac nasu rou,<text:line-break/>i-nciudat luleaua-i muc;<text:line-break/>Iepurele fuge puc.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Moului i vine-n minte<text:line-break/>Ca s-i ias nainte;<text:line-break/>Fuga-n raritea de tei:<text:line-break/>Iepurele e hei-hei!</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ei, ce faci tu, moulic,<text:line-break/>C n-ai mpucat nimic?<text:line-break/>Du-te-acas binior,<text:line-break/>C-i mai bine pe cuptor!</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Rndunelul</text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Un vnt i-o ploaie necjit<text:line-break/>S-au repezit ca din senin<text:line-break/>i rpie prelung pe frunze<text:line-break/>i-mi culc florile de crin.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Grdina toat-i rscolit...<text:line-break/>Ce trist e grdina mea!<text:line-break/>Pe-o creang tremur de fric<text:line-break/>Un pui plpnd de rndunic.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">E singur, n btaia ploaiei,<text:line-break/>i-n ciripitu-i rugtor<text:line-break/>mi spune s-i deschid fereastra:<text:line-break/>i eu deschid, el intr-n zbor.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">i iat-mi-l rotind prin cas<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i parc nu mai e pustiu<text:line-break/>n casa mea nveselit<text:line-break/>De ciripitul lui zglobiu.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dar iat... soarele s-arat...<text:line-break/>Pe frunze picurii sclipesc<text:line-break/>i rndunelele, pe-afar,<text:line-break/>n zboruri vesele vorbesc.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">La glasul lor, grbit, m las,<text:line-break/>Plpndul pui de rndunea...<text:line-break/>Mai vino, ploaie, nc-o dat<text:line-break/>S-l vd din nou n casa mea.</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Domnului A. Vlahu</text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="P32">Bine-ai venit,an nou!-Cu voie bun,<text:line-break/>ncreztori i-ngenunchem-nainte:<text:line-break/>Ne-aduci comoar de sperane sfinte,<text:line-break/>Ori prevestiri grozave de furtun?...<text:line-break/>De pretutindeni se ridic oapte<text:line-break/>i plns nbuit spre cel ce, ie,<text:line-break/>nduioat acum, i-a dat solie<text:line-break/>S luminezi odat trista noapte!</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P32">C sunt aici dureri nemrginite,<text:line-break/>Blesteme dureroase,-sunt copii<text:line-break/>Flmnzi i goi, i casele pustii,-<text:line-break/>Sunt cruci de lemn, la margine de sate...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P32">i mortii lor ateapt de la tine,<text:line-break/>An milostiv, n toate s fii darnic-<text:line-break/>i s le spuic n-au jertfit zadarnic<text:line-break/>Atta snge, gloanele haine.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P32">C-au ncetat slbaticele goane,-<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Iar dac sunt colibele cernite,<text:line-break/>Copii orfani i mame vduvite<text:line-break/>Nu vor mai plnge, sara, la icoane...</text:p>
    <text:list xml:id="list1181792865" text:style-name="L27">
     <text:list-header>
      <text:p text:style-name="P88">*</text:p>
     </text:list-header>
    </text:list>
    <text:p text:style-name="P32">Un glas pornit din inim curat,<text:line-break/>Un tnr glas te-ntmpin acum:<text:line-break/>Din largul rii spulber odat<text:line-break/>Mirosul greu de snge i de fum.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P32">An nou, an sfant,- adu belug n ar!<text:line-break/>Dar s nu lege-n ern sngerat<text:line-break/>Un rob spurcat, smna cea bogat...<text:line-break/>- An sfnt, adu-ni alt primvar!</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P32">S-nfrni, cu grija zilelor de mine,<text:line-break/>Nelegiuitul rs al lcomiei-<text:line-break/>i din prinosul roadelor cmpiei<text:line-break/>S se hrneasc cei ce ne dau pine.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P32">De fructe multe, pomii ncrcai<text:line-break/>i spicul greu de boabe s se rup!<text:line-break/>O, an frumos,-cu bogii astup<text:line-break/>Prpastia deschis ntre frai!...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P32">mpac vrajba sufletelor noastre!<text:line-break/>Nici plnsu-amar, nici blestemele gurii,<text:line-break/>Nici pumnii strni de vechiul foc al urii<text:line-break/>S n-amenine cerurile-albastre...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P32">Te-om preamri n laude, cu toii,<text:line-break/>O, an al pcii binefctoare!<text:line-break/>i-i vor aduce-n veacuri viitoare<text:line-break/>Prinosul lor de cinste, strnepoii!</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Bacilul lui Koch </text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Mult onorate doamne,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T28"><text:tab/><text:tab/><text:tab/></text:span>Distins auditor!<text:line-break/>La festival cnd vine, tot omul e dator<text:line-break/>S-asculte, nainte de partea amuzant,<text:line-break/>O conferin lung i foarte important.<text:line-break/>Conform acestei date sinistre, aadar,<text:line-break/>Avem ntre culise un confereniar,<text:line-break/>Un om cu greutate, un personagiu mare...<text:line-break/>S nu luai aceasta drept o ameninare!<text:line-break/>Dar ca s nu planeze asupra noastr vina<text:line-break/>C-am neglijat programul,  persoana cu pricina<text:line-break/>E gata s v in, un ceas i jumtate,<text:line-break/>O conferin grav de specialitate.<text:line-break/>Cum, nu v pare bine? De ce v-ai ntristat?<text:line-break/>Mai ateptai o clip, c doar n-am terminat.<text:line-break/>Pe de-alt parte, ns, gsind c-i anormal<text:line-break/>S v chemm la teatru... ca s-adormii n stal;<text:line-break/>C somnul, n aceste condiii verticale<text:line-break/>-att de izolate, nu face cinci parale;<text:line-break/>C nimene nu poate pretinde nimnui<text:line-break/>S-nghit festivalul cu conferina lui, <text:line-break/>Din spirit caritabil i din filantropie,<text:line-break/>tiind mai dinainte ce toat lumea tie,<text:line-break/>Cu voia dumneavoastr ne-abatem de la mod<text:line-break/>i-n loc de conferin, vei asculta o od.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Prea onorate doamne,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T28"><text:tab/><text:tab/></text:span>Distins auditor!<text:line-break/>Subiectul odei mele e-att de-ngrozitor<text:line-break/>C biata-mi Muz, alb de spaim i uimire,<text:line-break/>Cnd i-am cerut concursul, n loc s m inspire,<text:line-break/>S-a dat pe lng u, a pretextat ceva<text:line-break/>i-a disprut... adio! M-a prsit aa,<text:line-break/>Cu climara plin de noapte i de proz.<text:line-break/>E vorba de bacterii i de tuberculoz,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>E vorba de bacilul lui Koch...<text:line-break/>Precum vedei,<text:line-break/>Un subiect anume fcut pentru poei!<text:line-break/>O, nu v fie team... i dracul este negru<text:line-break/>Cnd st s-l zugrveasc un iconar integru,<text:line-break/>Dar... ici un pic de galben i dincolo puin<text:line-break/>Albastru... i pe gur o dung de carmin, <text:line-break/>Cu toate c-adineaori prea insuportabil,<text:line-break/>Din drac urt i negru devine acceptabil.<text:line-break/>(Dar nu fac oare zilnic cucoanele  i ele <text:line-break/>Cam tot acelai lucru pe propria lor piele?<text:line-break/>Ba fac aa chiar domnii  de genul femeiesc...)<text:line-break/>Bacilul despre care a vrea s v vorbesc<text:line-break/>Se afl-aici n sal... tiu bine c m-ascult,<text:line-break/>Dar nu vrea s-i trdeze prezena lui ocult.<text:line-break/>Intrarea n-a pltit-o fiindc-i mititel,<text:line-break/>Dar unde-i lume mult acolo e i el!<text:line-break/>Incognito ca regii i nepoftit ptrunde<text:line-break/>n orice fel de cas; l ntlneti oriunde:<text:line-break/>n berrii, pe strad, la cinematograf;<text:line-break/>i place s se joace cu ali bacili n praf;<text:line-break/>Se duce la plimbare cu trenul, cu tramvaiul,<text:line-break/>i peste tot se ine de bietul om ca scaiul,<text:line-break/>n fabric, la coal sau pe trotuar hai-hui, <text:line-break/>Dar peste tot i vede de-afacerile lui!<text:line-break/>i d ades pe credit persoana lui culant<text:line-break/>Cu o scaden lung, cnd nu e... galopant,<text:line-break/>Regia de tutunuri i face mult rabat;<text:line-break/>La buturi spirtoase e cointeresat;<text:line-break/>Din orice-abuz profit... La pnd, invizibil,<text:line-break/>n lupta mare-a vieii e mic, dar e teribil <text:line-break/>i chiar atunci cnd pare c doarme, e detept,<text:line-break/>La primrii el este consilier de drept<text:line-break/>i, tare-n atmosfera comunelor urbane,<text:line-break/>E cel mai mare duman al speciei umane...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Prea onorate doamne!<text:line-break/>Cnd in acest discurs,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Dac-ai vedea c intr n sal-aici un urs,<text:line-break/>N-ai nvli afar prin ui i prin ferestre<text:line-break/>Utiliznd cu toii resursele pedestre?<text:line-break/>De ce? Fiindc-i mare i foarte fioros...<text:line-break/>Bacilul lui Koch ns e mai primejdios!<text:line-break/>Dar fi&apos;ndc nu se vede i fi&apos;ndc e prea mic,<text:line-break/>Nu sperie pe nimeni...<text:line-break/>S judecm un pic.<text:line-break/>De-ar fi ct Himalaia ori numai ct aluna,<text:line-break/>Cnd tii c te omoar, mic-mare nu-i totuna?<text:line-break/>S-mi spunei dumneavostr: ce importan are<text:line-break/>Cnd un tlhar te-mpuc, dac e mic sau mare?<text:line-break/>O fi el mic, bacilul... da-i ru! Pe lng el,<text:line-break/>O biat matahal de urs e ca un miel.<text:line-break/>Ci oameni mor, de pild, n fiecare ar<text:line-break/>Mncai de uri? Trei-patru...<text:line-break/>Pe cnd aceast fiar,<text:line-break/>Acest vrjma de moarte al genului uman<text:line-break/>Atac i distruge pe fiecare an<text:line-break/>Nu zece, nu o sut... ci mii i mii de viei,<text:line-break/>Ci zeci de mii i sute de mii de tinerei<text:line-break/>C judecndu-l dup isprvile lui crunte<text:line-break/>i dup lcomie, apare ct un munte!<text:line-break/>Un monstru, un balaur ncolcit n spaiu<text:line-break/>Ce-nghite fr mil, nghite cu nesaiu<text:line-break/>i tot nu-i mai ajunge, tot nu mai e stul...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">*</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cu voia dumneavoastr, l-am insultat destul.<text:line-break/>Ar fi acum momentul s-l punem sub o lup<text:line-break/>S tim: ce form are i cu ce se ocup?<text:line-break/>Dup savani i medici ca doctorul Argon,<text:line-break/>Bacilul se prezint sub form de baston...<text:line-break/>Dar bolnavii, sraicii, spun doctorului Ciuc,<text:line-break/>C lor li se prezint sub form de mciuc!<text:line-break/>Ce-i el de fapt? Un zero, un fel de vrcolac<text:line-break/>Nici ct un ou de musc, nici ct un vrf de ac, <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Ceva aa, cilindric... Regret c nu gsesc<text:line-break/>O cret i-o tabel ca s vi-l zugrvesc. <text:line-break/>S-a zis c face parte din regnul vegetal,<text:line-break/>Dar eu nu cred... fiindc nu-mi pare natural<text:line-break/>S fie din aceeai familie cu floarea,<text:line-break/>S fie vr cu macul i rud cu cicoarea,<text:line-break/>Cu gingaa mimoz, cu palidul narcis...<text:line-break/>Ar nsemna c-i face familia de rs!<text:line-break/>Nu, nu prea are alur de plant  dimpotriv:<text:line-break/>Ai ntlnit vreodat o plant agresiv?<text:line-break/>Vzut-ai dumneavoastr o floare sau un pom<text:line-break/>S sar din grdin i s se dea la om?<text:line-break/>Ori ai putea concepe vreun fel de ciupercu<text:line-break/>Ce st s se rpead, cnd nimeni n-o asmu?...<text:line-break/>Dar, n sfrit, s-admitem c scrba asta mic<text:line-break/>Ar moteni-n caracter ceva de la urzic, <text:line-break/>Nu prea import regnul din care face parte<text:line-break/>Ct mai cu seam felul cum tie s se poarte.<text:line-break/>Distruge-n organisme esuturile vii;<text:line-break/>Se instaleaz n trupuri firave de copii;<text:line-break/>l poart-n nas i-n gur aproape-orice persoan.<text:line-break/>Dar el prefer pieptul de fat diafan<text:line-break/>(Dei nu-i prea rezist nici cei mai mari atlei).<text:line-break/>i  curios!  el are de mult pentru poei<text:line-break/>Un fel de slbiciune... s-ar zice c anume<text:line-break/>i place s distrug ce-i mai de pre pe lume!...<text:line-break/>De obicei, triete la umbr. Scos la soare,<text:line-break/>Devine melancolic i, cteodat, moare.<text:line-break/>Dar nu ntotdeauna. Uscat ca o mumie,<text:line-break/>Ades, de suprare, el cade-n letargie,<text:line-break/>Devine colb, se-nal pe-un strat de aer moale,<text:line-break/>Plutete-n atmosfer... i dnd mereu trcoale<text:line-break/>n jurul nostru, iari gsete un cotlon<text:line-break/>i cptnd via  devine iar baston!<text:line-break/>Savani-l studiaz fcnd din el culturi, <text:line-break/>Un fel de gelatin... un soi de rcituri<text:line-break/>Pe care stau microbii ca-n snul lui Avram<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i se-nmulesc acolo n voia lor...<text:line-break/>Uitam!<text:line-break/>El dragoste nu face. Cu omul n contrast,<text:line-break/>Bacilul lui Koch este surprinztor de cast.<text:line-break/>Dar cum se nmulete atunci? Prin ce minune?<text:line-break/> Prin sciziparitate sau prin diviziune:<text:line-break/>Se rupe-nti n dou... apoi se face-n patru...<text:line-break/>i-n nou luni e-n stare s-i umple acest teatru<text:line-break/>Cu fii, nepoi, nepoate, i socri mari, i frai,<text:line-break/>i veri, i verioare, i cuscri, i cumnai,<text:line-break/>C nici un fel de bab (de-a lor) n-ar fi n stare<text:line-break/>S-i spun a cui este i cte neamuri are!</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">*</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Prea onorate doamne!<text:line-break/>Doar cteva cuvinte,<text:line-break/>i-am isprvit... (v-asigur c nu mi-am pus n minte<text:line-break/>S v servesc bacilul lui Koch o noapte-ntreag).<text:line-break/>Cum toat lumea tie, microbul se propag<text:line-break/>Prin aer, prin contactul cu un bolnav n cas,<text:line-break/>Prin lapte i prin carne de vac ofticoas, <text:line-break/>Dar mai ales srutul, cnd cade pe-un teren<text:line-break/>Prielnic, rspndete agentul patogen.<text:line-break/>Deci n-ar fi ru, fiindc prudena e de aur,<text:line-break/>S v ferii din calea acestui mic balaur<text:line-break/>i orice om cuminte s cugete mai des<text:line-break/>C n-are nici o grab i nici un iteres<text:line-break/>S moar de ftizie...<text:line-break/>C poate s-i aleag o alt maladie<text:line-break/>Sau poate s-i dea singur n cap c-o crmid,<text:line-break/>n caz cnd existena i pare insipid;<text:line-break/>Dar dac-i place viaa i soarele, atunci<text:line-break/>E bine s respecte aceste vechi porunci,<text:line-break/>Pe care medicina de-un veac i le prescrie<text:line-break/>i dumenalui se face mereu c nu le tie:<text:line-break/>S nu stai toat ziua vrt cu nasu-n scripte,<text:line-break/>Iar laptele i carnea  s fie bine fripte.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>n orice alimente i-n orice butur<text:line-break/>S punei acid fenic  nu mult: o pictur...<text:line-break/>i cel puin o dat la dou sptmni<text:line-break/>Tot omul s se spele pe fa i pe mini...<text:line-break/>La pot sau la gar (i-n orice loc murdar)<text:line-break/>E obligat tot omul s scuipe-n buzunar,<text:line-break/>C pe podea nu-i voie dect n caz de boal...<text:line-break/>Iar cnd te duci la teatru sau intri n vreo coal<text:line-break/>i aerul de-acolo i pare echivoc,<text:line-break/>E mai recomandabil s nu respiri de loc...<text:line-break/>Acei ce au bronit sau tuse mgreasc,<text:line-break/>De semenii lor teferi grozav s se fereasc!<text:line-break/>S nu-i mai piard noaptea cu lucruri nepermise,<text:line-break/>S in toat iarna ferestrele deschise<text:line-break/>Iar vara s se duc la aer, la Sinaia,<text:line-break/>S steie-nchii n cas, c-afar-i ud ploaia...<text:line-break/>Pe lng asta-i bine, cnd suferi de-anemie,<text:line-break/>Cu propria ta via s faci economie.<text:line-break/>De nu vrei ca la urm s te trezeti mofluz,<text:line-break/>Evit surmenajul i orice fel de-abuz,<text:line-break/>Rrete-o cu tutunul, mai las butura!...<text:line-break/>Iar dac, din pcate, vrei s-i apropii gura<text:line-break/>De epiderma unei persoane din elit, <text:line-break/>Orict ar fi persoana accea de grbit,<text:line-break/>La locul ce urmeaz s fie srutat<text:line-break/>S dai nti c-o crp muiat-n sublimat.<text:line-break/>Ori, ca s fii mai siguri de via, eu v zic:<text:line-break/>Nu srutai nici mn, nici gur, nici... nimc!</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_1" text:outline-level="1">Postume</text:h>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Catren</text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Lunii</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Lun nou, corn de aur,<text:line-break/>Scump al nopilor tezaur,<text:line-break/>Subsemnatul  proletar<text:line-break/>N-am nimic n buzunar!</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Zi de var </text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Linite. Cldur. Soare.<text:line-break/>Slciile plngtoare<text:line-break/>Stau n aer, dormitnd.<text:line-break/>Un viel n ru s-adap<text:line-break/>i-o femeie, lng ap,<text:line-break/>Spal rufele, cntnd.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">i din vale abia vine<text:line-break/>Murmur slab, ca de albine,<text:line-break/>Somnoros i uniform:<text:line-break/>Rul, strlucind n soare,<text:line-break/>Ceart slciile, care<text:line-break/>Toat ziulica dorm.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Sub o salcie btrn<text:line-break/>i cu-o carte groas-n mn<text:line-break/>Care-mi ine de urt,<text:line-break/>M-am culcat n fn pe spate, <text:line-break/>Somnul lin, pe nechemate,<text:line-break/>A venit numaidect.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cntec, murmur, adiere<text:line-break/>De zefir n frunze piere<text:line-break/>i rmne doar un glas<text:line-break/>Care umple valea-ngust.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">............</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ia te uit, o lcust<text:line-break/>Mi-a srit tocmai pe nas!</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Mi-a rsrit n suflet dorul... </text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Mi-a rsrit n suflet dorul<text:line-break/>Ca o plpnd floare-albastr,<text:line-break/>i-ntr-un amurg de sear dulce<text:line-break/>A nflorit iubirea noastr, <text:line-break/>Dar tu te-ai ngrijit, iubito,<text:line-break/>Mai mult de floare, ca de glastr...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">n taina nopilor tcute,<text:line-break/>Cnd clipele se pierd mai greu,<text:line-break/>Eu am hrnit cu lacrimi floarea<text:line-break/>Ce-ntinerind cretea mereu,<text:line-break/>Dar azi chemnd uitarea sfnt<text:line-break/>Smulg floarea sufletului meu.</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>oaptele nopii</text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">ntrebam asear luna gnditoare:<text:line-break/> Dac prin poiene a rmas o floare<text:line-break/>Neculeas nc pentru draga mea, <text:line-break/>Dac sus, pe dealuri, pe poteci uitate,<text:line-break/>Pretutindeni unde m-ai vzut cu ea,<text:line-break/>Raza ta sfioas printre crengi strbate<text:line-break/>De-mi ncurc paii luminoase fire,<text:line-break/>Deteptnd n cale cte-o amintire, <text:line-break/>Dac pn-n ziu visurile trec<text:line-break/>Dar rmn n suflet,  pentru ce s plec?...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg"> Du-te-n lumea larg, pentru totdeauna,<text:line-break/>Trist i singur du-te, du-te! zice luna.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">i-ntrebai lumina sufletului meu:<text:line-break/> Dac fr dnsa timpul trece greu,<text:line-break/>Dac lng dnsa mi-i aa de bine,<text:line-break/>Spune-mi, suflet mndru, mpcat cu tine, <text:line-break/>Pentru ce, cnd toate lacrimile trec<text:line-break/>Fr nici o urm,  pentru ce s plec?...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Sufletu-mi rspunse:  Pe crri pustii,<text:line-break/>Du-te-n lumea larg. i s nu mai vii.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">i-ntrebai atuncea inima-mi trudit:<text:line-break/> Cea dinti, nebuno, czui n ispit,<text:line-break/>Singur-n tcere, tu eti vinovat<text:line-break/>C m cert cu mine i cu lumea toat.<text:line-break/>Cnd stelele nopii farmec nu mai au<text:line-break/>Fr ochii dragii,  pentru ce s stau?...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">i-mi rspunse-n oapt (o, inima mea!)<text:line-break/> Du-te-n lume singur. Eu rmn cu ea.</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Cntec</text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Florile uscate<text:line-break/>Care-mi stau n glastr,<text:line-break/>Florile uscate<text:line-break/>tiu povestea noastr.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">ntr-o diminea<text:line-break/>Le-ai adus grbit<text:line-break/>i-ntr-o diminea<text:line-break/>Ea mi-a fost iubit...</text:p>
    <text:list xml:id="list2718665806" text:style-name="L28">
     <text:list-header>
      <text:p text:style-name="P87">*</text:p>
      <text:p text:style-name="P111">i-a murit iubirea<text:line-break/>Ca o floare-n glastr,<text:line-break/>A murit iubirea<text:line-break/>naintea noastr.</text:p>
     </text:list-header>
    </text:list>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Doamnei Aftalion</text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Declar aici c, prin telepatie,<text:line-break/>O mn delicat mi-a trimis<text:line-break/>igri i zece lei ntr-o cutie <text:line-break/>i pentru toate astea dau n scris</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">C orice floare poate fi plantat<text:line-break/>ntr-un pmnt strin  dar, n sfrit,<text:line-break/>Ea n-o s-i uite patria vreodat, <text:line-break/>Grdina mndr-n care-a rsrit...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Deci pentru mine are importan<text:line-break/>Nu darul, ci pornirea care d.<text:line-break/>De-aceea, scump doamn, v rog s...<text:line-break/>S nu-mi luai poezia drept chitan!</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>V dau i eu n schimb aceste glume, <text:line-break/>Primii-le c-un zmbet, doamna mea...<text:line-break/>Cea mai frumoas fat de pe lume<text:line-break/>Nu d dect ce are... chiar cnd vrea!</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Doamnei Ermosa Aftalion</text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">O amintire, doamna mea,<text:line-break/>E ca un vag parfum de floare.<text:line-break/>Cu ct te deprtezi de ea,<text:line-break/>Cu-att se-ntunec i moare.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Pe cnd imaginile vii<text:line-break/>Rmn frumoase dup moarte,<text:line-break/>Ca nite fluturi argintii<text:line-break/>Fixai cu acul ntr-o carte.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Primete dar acest album<text:line-break/>n care-am aruncat pe pagini<text:line-break/>Tristeea zilelor de-acum<text:line-break/>Topit-n vesele imagini.</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Catren</text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">O, de ce nu sunt o floare,<text:line-break/>Un lstun purtat de vnt, <text:line-break/>Ca s uit o clip numai<text:line-break/>Unde eti  i unde snt!...</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>La neige </text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Que de fois, mon amour, auprs du feu qui tremble,<text:line-break/>Pntrs par les doux regrets du jour mourant,<text:line-break/>Nous restmes rveurs  regarder ensemble<text:line-break/>Les grands flocons de neige qui tombaient lentement...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Maintenant je suis seul, hlas! Le jour se pme...<text:line-break/>Et je souris (combien plus triste quautrefois!)<text:line-break/>Aux doux regrets dantan qui tombaient sur nos mes<text:line-break/>Comme les grands flocons de neige, sur les toits!</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Le papillon </text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Je fis un voeu tendre:<text:line-break/>Je cueilllerai la fleur<text:line-break/>O il va descendre,<text:line-break/>Pour gurir mon coeur.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Il vole, il hsite,<text:line-break/>Il monte, il descend <text:line-break/>Puis pose un instant,<text:line-break/>Sur ta main petite,<text:line-break/>Son vol inconstant.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">O, la belle offrande,<text:line-break/>La petite fleur!<text:line-break/>Je te la demande<text:line-break/>Pour gurir mon coeur...</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">omerul</text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Umblnd n sus i-n jos pe bulevard,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>A poposit la umbr sub un gard,<text:line-break/>i-i trist fiindc nimeni nu-l ntreab<text:line-break/>Dac-a mncat ori dac are treab...</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Proz</text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ce muritor e omul din popor!<text:line-break/>De cnd exist aburi i benzin,<text:line-break/>Eu nu cunosc ceva mai muritor<text:line-break/>Ca omul, cnd l calc o main...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">i ia-ntr-o zi nevasta i biatul<text:line-break/>Sau fata,<text:line-break/>i pleac cu acceleratul.<text:line-break/>Dar la un pod stricat, la un tunel,<text:line-break/>O roat sare de pe linie... i, gata!<text:line-break/>S-a isprvit cu el.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Te uii la altul cum adun bani,<text:line-break/>Parc-am tri un milion de ani.<text:line-break/>Dar ntr-o bun zi, te miri ce-l doare,<text:line-break/>i cnd s zic bodaproste,  moare.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ce n-a fcut maina, face boala<text:line-break/>i tot acolo iese socoteala...</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Autorului Hronicului Mscriciului Vltuc</text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cnd trece-n zbor aeroplanu&apos;<text:line-break/>i vd c-l latr un cel<text:line-break/>mi vine-n minte Pstorel<text:line-break/>Cum critic pe Toprceanu.</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Bimbiriichel</text:h>
    <text:h text:style-name="P58" text:outline-level="4">I</text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="P113">................</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P112">Fraii lui, biei i fete,<text:line-break/>Au crescut mai pe-ndelete,<text:line-break/>Toi plngoci i dolofani.<text:line-break/>Cel mai tnr dintre apte<text:line-break/>Se numete Pap-lapte<text:line-break/>i-a-mplinit abia doi ani.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Toat ziulica ip <text:line-break/>Nu st locului o clip,<text:line-break/>(Cere lapte), vrei-nu vrei.<text:line-break/>Biata m-sa la tot pasul<text:line-break/>Trebuie s-i tearg nasul<text:line-break/>i s-l aib-n grija ei.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">N-au nici capr, n-au nici vac.<text:line-break/>Mama-i vduv srac.<text:line-break/>Numai Bimbiriichel<text:line-break/>O ajut cteodat<text:line-break/>Cnd o vede suprat...<text:line-break/>Ce s-ar face fr el?</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4">II</text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="P32">ntr-o sear, o vecin<text:line-break/>Zice:  Vin de la grdin,<text:line-break/>Dintr-o margine de sat.<text:line-break/>M dusesem, eu cu fata,<text:line-break/>i-am luat i pe cumnata,<text:line-break/>S culegem zarzavat.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P32"><text:soft-page-break/>Dar nici nu intrasem bine:<text:line-break/>De sub gard, de lng mine<text:line-break/>t! un iepure oldan!<text:line-break/>Arz-l focul s mi-l arz,<text:line-break/>Mi-a mncat un car de varz,<text:line-break/>Toat munca dintr-un an!...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P32">Bimbiriichel deoparte<text:line-break/>St uitndu-se-ntr-o carte,<text:line-break/>Parc nici n-ar auzi<text:line-break/>Chestia cu zarzavatul...<text:line-break/>Dar a doua zi, biatul<text:line-break/>S-a sculat n zori de zi.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P32">Unde pleac? La grdina<text:line-break/>Unde ieri a fost vecina,<text:line-break/>ntr-o margine de sat, <text:line-break/>C-i fcuse noaptea planul<text:line-break/>Cum s prind el oldanul<text:line-break/>Care fur zarzavat.</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Fabule pentru copii</text:h>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4">Bivolul i coofana </text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Pe spinarea unui bivol mare, negru, fioros,<text:line-break/>Se plimba o coofan<text:line-break/>Cnd n sus i cnd n jos.<text:line-break/>Un cel trecnd pe-acolo s-a oprit mirat n loc:<text:line-break/> Ah, ce mare dobitoc!<text:line-break/>Nu-l credeam aa de prost<text:line-break/>S ia-n spate pe oricine...<text:line-break/>Ia stai, frate, c e rost<text:line-break/>S m plimbe i pe mine!</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Cugetnd aa, se trage ndrt s-i fac vnt,<text:line-break/>Se pitete la pmnt<text:line-break/>i de-odat  zdup!  i sare<text:line-break/>Bivolului n spinare...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ce s-a ntmplat pe urm nu e greu de-nchipuit.<text:line-break/>Apucat cam fr veste, bivolul a tresrit,<text:line-break/>Dar i-a fost destul o clip s se scuture, i-apoi<text:line-break/>S-l rstoarne,<text:line-break/>S-l ia-n coarne<text:line-break/>i ct colo s-l arunce, ca pe-o zdrean n trifoi.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg"> Ce-ai gndit tu oare, javr? Au, crezut-ai c sunt mort?<text:line-break/>Coofana, treac-mearg, pe spinare o suport<text:line-break/>C m apr de mute, de nari i de tuni<text:line-break/>i de alte spurcciuni...<text:line-break/>Pe cnd tu, potaie proast, cam ce slujb poi s-mi faci?<text:line-break/>Nu mi-ar fi ruine mie de viei i de malaci,<text:line-break/>Bivol mare i puternic, gospodar cu greutate,<text:line-break/>S te port degeaba-n spate?...</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4">ntrebare i rspuns </text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Rumegnd cocenii de pe lng jug,<text:line-break/>S-a-ntrebat odat boul de la plug:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg"> Doamne, pe cnd alii huzuresc mereu,<text:line-break/>Pentru ce eu singur s muncesc din greu?...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">La-ntrebarea asta, un prelung ecou<text:line-break/>I-a rspuns din slav:<text:line-break/> Pentru c eti bou...</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:soft-page-break/>Boierul i argatul </text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Un boier, clare pe-o frumoas iap,<text:line-break/>Trebuind s treac ntr-un loc o ap<text:line-break/>Peste-o punte-ngust  i fiind grbit,<text:line-break/>i-a chemat argatul i i-a poruncit:<text:line-break/> Ia-mi n spate iapa<text:line-break/>i mi-o trece apa!<text:line-break/> Nu pot, zise omul lsnd nasu-n jos.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg"> Hm! fcu boierul foarte mnios:<text:line-break/>Leneul la toate<text:line-break/>Zice c nu poate...</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4">Leul deghizat </text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Leul s-a-mbrcat odat<text:line-break/>ntr-o piele de mgar,<text:line-break/>S colinde ara toat<text:line-break/>Din hotar pn-n hotar,<text:line-break/>Ca s vad cum se poart lupii (marii dregtori)<text:line-break/>Cu noroadele-i blajine de supui rumegtori.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Deci, trecnd el ntr-o sear la o margine de crng<text:line-break/>Ca un biet mgar ntng,<text:line-break/>Nite lupi, cum l vzur, se reped la el pe loc<text:line-break/>i-ntr-o clip l nfac, grmdindu-l la mijloc.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg"> Stai, mieilor! Ajunge,  c v rup n dini acui!<text:line-break/>(Strig leul, aprndu-i pielea cea adevrat.)<text:line-break/>Astfel v purtai voi oare cu iubiii mei supui?...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Lupii, cunoscndu-i glasul, ndrt s-au tras pe dat,<text:line-break/>i de fric se fcur mici, ca nite celui.<text:line-break/> O, mria-ta! Iertare!<text:line-break/>Zise cel mai diplomat, <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Semnai aa de tare<text:line-break/>C-un mgar adevrat!...</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Fabule mici pentru oameni mari</text:h>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4">Omul i raa </text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Unui om, sracul, ntr-o diminea,<text:line-break/>I-a murit o ra,<text:line-break/>Bietul om, de ciud, tare s-a-ntristat,<text:line-break/>Cnd vzu c-i moart cu adevrat.<text:line-break/>Dar la scurt vreme, n aceeai lun,<text:line-break/>I-a murit i soacra  tot de moarte bun...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Morala:</text:span><text:line-break/>S nu pierzi ndejdea, orice-ar fi s fie:<text:line-break/>Dup ntristare, vine bucurie.</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4">Doi prieteni </text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Un beiv din lumea toat<text:line-break/>(Care se numete Nae),<text:line-break/>Ce fusese rupt odat<text:line-break/>De nevast-sa-n btaie,<text:line-break/>Auzind cum c nevasta unui prieten i-a crpit<text:line-break/>i aceluia o palm, foarte mult s-a veselit...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Morala:</text:span><text:line-break/>Rde ruptul de crpit.</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:soft-page-break/>Cin&apos; s-a fript cu ciorb... </text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Fratele nevestei unui negustor<text:line-break/>A venit odat pe la casa lor,<text:line-break/>Zicnd c la noapte, mine, cine tie,<text:line-break/>Are gnd s plece n cltorie<text:line-break/>i c, prin urmare,<text:line-break/>Vrea s-i srute sora la plecare.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg"> Ba s nu pui gura pe nevasta mea,<text:line-break/>A strigat brbatul, c intri-n belea!<text:line-break/> i de ce s nu pun gura, mi cumnate,<text:line-break/>Cnd tii c mi-e sor i c eu i-s frate?<text:line-break/> Poi s-i fii i tat! zise omul scurt, <text:line-break/>Cin&apos; s-a fript cu ciorb sufl i-n iaurt.</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4">Vduva i piticul </text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Zice c demult, odat,<text:line-break/>Un pitic s-a nsurat<text:line-break/>Cu o vduv bogat,<text:line-break/>Ce fusese mritat<text:line-break/>Cu un mare om de stat.<text:line-break/>i-o fi dus ea, altdat, o via mai tihnit,<text:line-break/>Dar la urm i piticul a fcut-o fericit...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cu munc i cu rbdare,<text:line-break/>Poi face ct unul mare.</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4">Mgarul n grev </text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Un mgar s-a pus n grev, nu se tie pentru ce...<text:line-break/>Eti folositor, vezi bine,<text:line-break/>Dar s nu crezi c pe lume nu se poate fr tine.</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:soft-page-break/>Microscopic</text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cnd pleca odat la rzboi un om,<text:line-break/>I-a strigat o cioar dintr-un vrf de pom:<text:line-break/> Du-te la btaie, pentru ar mori,<text:line-break/>i-i va da nevasta un copil din flori.<text:line-break/>Omul,<text:line-break/>Auzind acestea, n-a mai vrut s plece,<text:line-break/>Deci a fost la urm, fiindc-a dezertat,<text:line-break/>Condamnat la moarte i executat.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Morala:</text:span><text:line-break/>Cine crede tot ce-i spui<text:line-break/>Este vai de capul lui.</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Plou... </text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Pe-aici cnd plou, plou ndesat,<text:line-break/>Nu ine ca la noi un ceas ori dou.<text:line-break/>C ziua plou, plou pe-nserat,<text:line-break/>i cnd se crap iar de ziu,  plou.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">n faptul zilei, streinile plng.<text:line-break/>Pdurea st plouat ca o curc.<text:line-break/>Natura calc cu piciorul stng:<text:line-break/>Pe-aici cnd plou,  plou, nu se-ncurc!</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Iar cnd s-arat soarele srac.<text:line-break/>De dup nouri, ca s-i fac-n ciud,<text:line-break/>N-apuci a scoate nasul din cerdac,<text:line-break/>C pn la ntoarcere,  te ud.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Exist i rstimpuri cnd se moaie,<text:line-break/>Cnd parc nu mai toarn-aa, de sus,<text:line-break/>i cerul cte-oleac, spre apus,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Se lumineaz puintel  a ploaie.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Atunci se cheam c e timp frumos<text:line-break/>(Mcar c tot mai cade-un pic de bur),<text:line-break/>Dar fumul din ogeac se las-n jos,<text:line-break/>i porcul umbl tot cu paiu-n gur...</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Roman n stil vechi </text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Se stinge amurgul cu roii vpi,<text:line-break/>i noaptea de var<text:line-break/>Coboar-n tcere pe muni i pe vi,<text:line-break/>nalt i clar.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">La marginea apei s-i caute vad<text:line-break/>O turm s-abate.<text:line-break/>Rsare i luna din codri de brad,<text:line-break/>n singurtate.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Micuele-n umbra prerii de ru<text:line-break/>Se duc s se culce;<text:line-break/>Din vale s-aude un glas de pru<text:line-break/>Slbatic i dulce.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Odihna s-aterne pe sfntul lca<text:line-break/>Din vremea strbun.<text:line-break/>i numai o fat cu dor ptima<text:line-break/>Mai cnt sub lun.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Iubitul i-ateapt s-o prind n bra<text:line-break/>La poal de munte,<text:line-break/>i lung s-o srute cu dulce nesa,<text:line-break/>Pe ochi i pe frunte.</text:p>
    <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Din tren </text:h>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ca un val de cer senin<text:line-break/>Prins n volbur nomad<text:line-break/>Curge vntul cristalin<text:line-break/>Pe cmpia de zpad.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="lg">Fr urm, fr el,<text:line-break/>Gndul meu pierdut alearg<text:line-break/>La ntrecere cu el,<text:line-break/>i se pierde-n zarea larg.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P52"/>
   </text:section>
